text2:
轻机枪是一种历史悠久且廉价易得的近程速射武器。贯穿整个太空战斗史，轻机枪就一直都被用来在近距离内对抗来袭的导弹与战斗机。但在面对拥有良好装甲的目标时效果不佳。

由于易于制造，轻机枪在星域中拥有着数百种不同的型号，即便这些武器的机械原理千差万别，但凡是使用化学发射药以超过{1200}发每分的射速发射动能弹头的武器都被归类为舰载轻机枪。

因为弹药的开销很低，所以流行于各种小型民用舰船当中。因弹头外包裹有高熔点金属，允许其枪口初速更快，并在近距离内产生惊人的动能伤害。
text1_095:
A venerable low-cost, readily available rapid fire weapon which has been used effectively versus missiles and fighters at short range throughout the history of combat in space. It is nearly useless versus properly armored targets.

Due to ease of manufacture, hundreds of models exist in the Sector. Any weapon that employs chemical propellant to fire inert projectiles at over 1200 rounds per minute can be classified as a light ship-mounted machine gun, but beyond that the mechanisms that drive the actions of these weapons vary considerably. 

Popular with small civilian craft due to low cost ammunition. Projectiles jacketed with metals that have a high melting point allow greater muzzle velocity and deliver a surprisingly large amount of kinetic energy at close-range.

由于易于制造，轻机枪在星域中拥有着数百种不同的型号，即便这些武器的机械原理千差万别，但凡是使用化学发射药以超过{1200}发每分的射速发射动能弹头的武器都被归类为舰载轻机枪。

因为弹药的开销很低，所以流行于各种小型民用舰船当中。因弹头外包裹有高熔点金属，允许其枪口初速更快，并在近距离内产生惊人的动能伤害。

text2:
轻机枪的双管升级版。虽然它无法有效对付装甲目标，但自人类太空战斗史展开以来，它就已经担任着反导弹与反战机的任务。

作为一种速射小口径动能武器的连装版本，因其在拦截导弹与战机时的优秀表现而被星域中的大多数飞行员们所熟知。

由于双管轻机枪可在近距离内对敌舰护盾倾斜大量动能弹而致其反应堆迅速过载，而这正是那些缺乏战斗经验的菜鸟舰长所经常忽视的一种有效战术。
text1_095:
An upgraded, twin barrel version of the venerable light machine gun. Not effective against armored targets, but has excelled in an anti-missile and fighter role since the dawn of human space combat.

This is a dual mount of the same rapid fire, inert, low-caliber chemical projectile weapon known to every pilot in the Sector. An excellent point defense mount, which excels in both a missile interdiction and anti-fighter role. 

The large amount of kinetic energy delivered to shield systems of enemy craft at close-range typically causes emitter overload, a tactical option often overlooked by inexperienced captains.

text2:
尽管这种老式武器只能以低射速发射低初速的近程破甲弹，但较低的幅能需求正是它能被沿用至今的唯一理由。

光从其蓝图就不难看出，轻型迫击炮在设计之初可能并未考虑过被安装在星舰之上。但在后续发展中通过在后膛装填装置进行的一些巧妙地改装，使得它得以能在大气层外安装并正常使用。在实战中,轻型迫击炮糟糕的转速和射速让它难以威胁到移动或者带护盾的目标。尽管如此，它还是经常被用于训练菜鸟炮手，以便让他们更好地掌握宇宙弹道学中的战术和术语。

如今这种轻便廉价的武器正被广泛应用于私人星舰或独行的星际飞行器上。
text1_095:
An antiquated weapon that fires anti-armor rounds at a low rate of fire, muzzle velocity, and range. Its low flux buildup is a lone saving grace.

The weapon blueprints for Light Mortars actually did not intend them for spacecraft at all, but an ingenious modification to the breech loading mechanism permits installation and use outside an atmospheric environment. In combat, there is little the Light Mortar can do versus moving or shielded targets due to its terrible mount rotation and rate of fire. Nonetheless, it is often used for training novice gunnery officers in the finer points of space ballistic tactics and nomenclature.

Commonly fitted on private yachts and solo interplanetary vehicles because it is so light and cheap.

text2:
拥有比表亲更高射速且能发射更大破甲弹的老式武器。尽管炮弹初速与射程较差,但较低的幅能需求正是它被沿用至今的唯一理由。

这种最初设计于行星地表作战的重型武器，其表面上是为了摧毁地面防御工事,但在城市轰炸中却发挥了更大的作用。由于机构简单且坚固耐用，因此只需替换自动测距仪与瞄准模块，就可使其在大气层外安装并正常使用。事实证明，用该武器来对付没有护盾且移动缓慢的目标时效果最佳。
text1_095:
An antiquated weapon that fires larger anti-armor rounds at a somewhat higher rate of fire than its smaller cousin. Projectile speed is low and effective range is short. Low flux buildup is a lone saving grace.

The Heavy Mortar was originally designed for use in planetary surface combat. Ostensibly intended for cracking fortifications, it saw far more use in urban bombardment. The robust internal mechanisms permit installation and use outside an atmospheric environment with only minor adjustments, notably replacement of the automatic rangefinder/targeting module. If employed against a large, unshielded, and slow-moving target, the heavy mortar can prove most effective.

text2:
能在贴身距离内对导弹与战机造成毁灭性打击的速射武器。但如果长期持续开火，其精度也会急剧下降。

由于这种经典的多管速射武器平台内配备有先进的计算装置，导致该武器通常是由拥有{霸主}授权的自动工厂代工完成。常使用带有贫铀弹尖的实心弹头，虽不具爆炸性，但多管设计所产生的极高射速,使其在牺牲幅能成本的前提下，对近距离内的小型移动目标拥有着不俗的拦截效率。
text1_095:
A rapid fire weapon that is especially devastating to missiles and fighters at point-blank range. Accuracy degrades sharply during prolonged bursts. 

An advanced timing mechanism beats in the heart of this multi-barrel weapon platform, generally manufactured only by licensed Hegemony Autofactories. Rounds typically use depleted uranium tips and are non explosive. Multiple barrels enable an extremely high rate of fire, which comes at a cost in flux.
text1_091:

text2:
射程优秀的小口径自动加农炮，旨在削弱敌舰护盾，尤其是在对付反应堆较弱的目标时效果最佳。

拥有自动装填与水冷系统的小口径武器，善于发射高速动能弹来在中远程交战中过载敌舰护盾。

适用于在小型舰船上提供火力支援。但极低的炮台转速，使它无法胜任反导和反战机任务。
text1_095:
A small caliber autocannon with a good range for such a light weapon. Designed to weaken enemy shields, especially effective against weaker generators.

Usually manufactured with small bores perfect for medium- to long-range. The weapon fires high velocity kinetic rounds designed to overload enemy shields with ease. Features an autoloader and is liquid cooled. 

Excellent fire support weapon for smaller craft.  Poor mount turn rate makes it a bad choice vs fighters and missiles.
text1_091:

text2:
轻型自动加农炮的双管版本。这种优秀的密接支援武器，能有效削弱敌舰的护盾系统。

这种适用于中远程交战的小口径武器，通过简洁巧妙的机械设计，在排出两倍于标准版数量弹壳的前提下，排除抛壳口被卡住的风险。与单管版本一致的是，该武器同样具备自动装填机与水冷系统,且仍善于利用发射的高速动能弹头来过载敌舰护盾。
text1_095:
A double barreled version of the Light AC. An excellent weapon for close-range support, and quite effective at bringing shields down.

Usually manufactured with small bores perfect for medium to long-range. An ingeniously elegant mechanical design prevents ejection ports from being jammed while expelling twice as many spent shell casings as the standard chassis. Like the single barrel version, the weapon fires high velocity rounds designed to punch through enemy shields. Autoloader and liquid cooling systems are identical to the single barrel version.

text2:
用于近距离作战的小口径加农炮。优秀的射速使它能有效对付装甲。

为强调安全性，这种发射高爆弹头的小口径加农炮，通过内置冷却系统与自动装填器，来防止在高幅能下发生弹药殉爆。有趣的是，那些总想证明些什么的驱逐舰舰长很喜欢这个小玩意...
text1_095:
A small caliber cannon designed for close-range fights, excellent versus armor and with a superb fire rate.

Small caliber cannon designed to fire high-explosive rounds. Design of the coolant systems and autoloader emphasizes safety and prevention of cook-off potentially caused by high flux levels. Favored by destroyer captains that have something to prove.
text1_091:
A small caliber cannon designed for close-range fights, excellent versus armor and with a superb fire rate.

text2:
它能发射一连串依靠投放者惯性滑行，且配有近炸引信的小炸弹。

这种简单的三联装发射管，通过持续发射几十枚{Mk.VI}型破片炸弹来打击敌舰。尽管不具备制导与推近系统,且所谓的敌我识别完全依靠投射方的瞄准器,但它却能利用庞大的数量优势来覆盖大片区域，并在近炸引信被敌机触发时引爆,来产生类似防空炮的效果，以暂时在该位置生成防空拦截区。
text1_095:
Releases a cluster of free-floating bomblets that retain the momentum of the launching craft. The bomblets are equipped with a proximity fuse.

A Frag Bomb projector fires Mark VI fragmentation bomblets from three tubes. Unguided and without a propulsion system, the bomblets rely on a friend-or-foe targeting system. Their vast numbers allow them to cover a wide swath of space, effectively creating a Point Defense barrier in that location, albeit for a limited time. When the proximity fuse is triggered by an enemy craft, the bomblet will detonate, achieving similar effects to those of flak weapons.

text2:
释放一群依靠惯性飘浮的高爆炸弹,能有效摧毁缺乏点防的低速目标。

这种拥有三联装发射管的集束炸弹投射器，旨在持续发射几十枚完全依赖惯性飘浮的，且无制导、敌我识别与推近系统的{Mk.II}型高爆炸弹来打击敌舰，这些集束炸弹不仅能有效威胁缺乏护盾的老旧星舰，其惊人的投放量，也能起到区域封锁与正面压制的作用。
text1_095:
Releases a cluster of free-floating, high-explosive bomblets. More effective versus unshielded and slow-moving targets.

A Cluster Bomb projector is equipped with three tubes designed to fire dozens of Mark II Explosively Formed Penetrator bomblets. The bomblets are unguided and have no propulsion system, relying on the initial momentum of the strike craft to engage the target. They are equipped with a friend-or-foe targeting scanner, and will only detonate when impacting an appropriate target. The shaped charge explosive is highly effective versus unshielded targets. The sheer number of bomblets that can be deployed by this weapon system is staggering, and as such it makes the Cluster Bomb a useful area denial weapon.
text1_091:

这种拥有三联装发射管的集束炸弹投射器，旨在持续发射几十枚完全依赖惯性飘浮的，且无制导、敌我识别与推近系统的{Mk.II}型高爆炸弹来打击敌舰，这些集束炸弹不仅能有效威胁缺乏护盾的老旧星舰，其惊人的投放量，也能起到区域封锁与正面压制的作用。

text2:
久经考验的武器系统，其弹舱所携带的大量高爆弹头是依靠发射者那得到的速度飞向目标。

每个炸弹舱都装配有若干枚能逐一发射的{Comp-X}高爆炸弹。由于这些炸弹没有推进系统，而只能依赖从发射者那得到的速度飞向目标{(即，俯冲轰炸)。此外这项设计中所整合的热屏障也能使这些脆弱的炸弹能在敌方点防火力网下存活更久。
text1_095:
A tried and tested weapon system, the bomb bay holds multiple warheads that rely on the velocity of the launching craft to reach their target.

Each bomb bay is equipped with several non guided high-explosive Comp-X bombs that can be released one at a time. The bombs have no propulsion system and are dependent on the velocity of the launching craft to carry them to target (i.e., dive bombing).  Atmospheric shielding intrinsic to the design also gives the bombs a high Time To Live in an hostile Point-Defense environment.
text1_091:
A tried and tested weapon system, the bomb bay holds multiple warheads that rely on the velocity of the launching craft to reach their target.

Each bomb bay is equipped with several non guided high-explosive Comp-X bombs that can be released one at a time. The bombs have no propulsion system and are dependent on the velocity of the launching craft to carry them to target (i.e., dive bombing).  Atmospheric shielding intrinsic to the design also gives the bombs a high Time To Live in an hostile Point-Defense environment.
text1_091cn:
久经考验的武器系统，其弹舱所携带的大量高爆弹头是依靠发射者那得到的速度飞向目标。

每个炸弹舱都装配有若干枚能逐一发射的{Comp-X}高爆炸弹。由于这些炸弹没有推进系统，而只能依赖从发射者那得到的速度飞向目标{(即，俯冲轰炸)。此外这项设计中所整合的热屏障也能使这些脆弱的炸弹能在敌方点防火力网下存活更久。

text2:
能以爆发性速度发射大量小型箭弹。体积虽小，却能在单次开火下迅速击溃绝大多数护盾系统，但对装甲却没有任何效果。

发射无壳箭弹的小口径火炮。其令人过目难忘的供弹系统，能以每秒数百发的速度投射'针刺'。因不需要退壳机构，而由此富余下来的空间则安装了额外的冷却系统，以进一步提高射速。
text1_095:
Fires bursts of small flechettes at a high rate of fire. The volume of fire can quickly overwhelm shield projectors, but is generally ineffective against armor.

A Light Needler is a small-bore flechette gun, designed to fire caseless ammunition. Features an impressive feed system which can deliver hundreds of "needles" per second. There is no need for an ejector system, and the resulting space availability is instead used to provide additional cooling units, vastly enhancing the rate of fire. 

Domain Naval doctrine holds that the weapon is to be used on enemy shields at long-range, but in a pinch, gunnery officers will train their Needlers on enemy fighter wings and long-range missile threats.

text2:
轻型自动炮的一种高科技改良版本，能更精确的发射中程金属弹头，与前者同样擅长压制敌舰的护盾系统。

作为高斯炮的微缩变种版，而采用了相同的电磁发射技术，以获得优秀的精度与射程，且在不开火时，炮台的转速也非常之快。

对于炮手而言，在幅能充足的情况下，轨道炮将比轻型自动炮更胜一筹。
text1_095:
A high-tech improvement of the Autocannon, the railgun fires accurate, medium-range slugs. Like the AC, it excels at overwhelming enemy shield generators.

A miniaturized version of the Gauss Cannon, the railgun relies on a strong magnetic field to fire shells at high velocities. The accuracy and range are excellent, and the turret is able to rotate quickly while not firing. 

The railgun is preferred to the Autocannon by gunnery officers that have ample flux capacity at their disposal.

text2:
这种旋转加农炮有着巨量的工程规范说明以确保它良好的可靠性和可操作性。不过星域中在海军服役的武器官一直在唾弃那些随这种武器而传播开来的糟糕维护习惯。

善于利用冰雹般小型破片弹来撕碎导弹与战机。虽幅能需求不高，但对装甲和护盾效果欠佳。
text1_095:
A rotatory cannon with generous engineering specifications which provide for great ease of operation and reliability. Weapons officers across the professional navies of the Sector, meanwhile, curse the Thumper for rewarding poor maintenance habits. 

Shreds enemy missiles and fighters with an overwhelming hail of small payload, medium velocity fragmentation rounds. Although flux-efficient, this weapon system has little effect against armor and shields.
text1_091:

text2:
能发射装有近炸引信的破片榴弹，以最大限度地对抗战机与导弹。

在'大崩塌'前那令人陶醉的年代里，该武器系统就随着小型廉价战机，特别是扮演打击角色战机的迅速崛起，而越发常见。其发射装有近炸引信的榴弹，能在爆炸时将大量弹片扩散至很大的范围之内,以产生很大的典型目标杀伤半径。而最新型号还在火控系统内固化有{Mk.VI}轨迹预测系统。
text1_095:
A defensive weapon system that fires shrapnel-filled shells equipped with a proximity fuse for maximum effect against fighters and missiles.

The rising prominence of small, cheap fighter craft, especially in the strike role, led to a wider deployment of this weapons system in the heady days pre-Collapse. Fires ballistic rounds fitted with a proximity fuse. The resulting explosion sends a hail of flechettes in a wide area with a respectable kill radius versus standard targets. Newer models feature a fire control system hardwired into a Mark VI Predictor.
text1_091:

text2:
作为那些无处不在的速射机枪类武器的大兄弟，重机枪能有效地对付各种中小型目标。

作为星域中大部分巡逻船只值得信赖的选择，其使用的可靠气体反冲式机制，以及用于开栓清洁用的主动弹药自燃保险和防双弹保护，甚至可以追溯到古老的地球时代。通常被安装在一处较重的底座上以吸收长时间连续射击产生的后坐力，虽武器口径有一定的变化，但自动工厂仍能轻松制造。

因这些更重的弹头不像较轻的弹头那样在冲击中碎裂,而足以威胁到护卫舰的舰体。虽射速不如火神炮,但出色的精度让它足以担负点防御的重任。
text1_095:
A larger cousin of the ubiquitous rapid-fire machine gun category of weapons, the Heavy MG is effective against both small and medium-sized targets.

A workhorse of patrol craft across the Sector, this weapons system features reliable blowback firing mechanism said to date back to the days of Old Earth. Safety features include a positive cook-off safety for open bolt clearing and double ram prevention. The weapon is typically mounted on a relatively heavy base to help absorb recoil during prolonged bursts of fire. Calibers vary within a moderate range and ammunition is easily fabricated by standard forges. 

The heavier projectiles do not shatter upon impact like lighter ammunition and present a credible threat to frigate-class vessels. Extremely accurate, though slower-firing than a vulcan cannon. Excels in a point-defense role.

text2:
能造成相较于尺寸而言高伤害的一种陈旧的武器设计。其发射的动能炮弹在用来对付敌舰护盾时相当有效。

由于在'大崩塌'期间，大部分重型巡逻舰都安装有劲弩{Mk.I}武器平台，而这刚好解释了为什么劲弩自动炮被认为是该星域回收率最高的武器系统的原因。由于冷却系统过于陈旧且自动抛壳机的缺失，而导致其射速与可靠性相当糟糕。

其唯一被沿用至今的理由大概是其无处不在的蓝图，以及在对付护盾时的特效性。如今这些炮弹为何如此有效的原因尽管尚不明朗，但有人猜测这些炮弹外壳内可能蕴藏着意料外的电磁特性。
text1_095:
An antiquated weapon design with high per-shot damage for its size. The kinetic shells are especially effective versus enemy shields.

Heavier patrol craft at the time of the Collapse were mostly fitted with the Arbalest Mk I weapons platform; this likely explains why the Arbalest is claimed to be among the most scavenged ship weapon systems in the Sector. The primitive cooling system and a lack of an autoejector hamper rate of fire and reliability. 

The only redeeming feature is the ubiquity of blueprints for the arbalest round, which is effective at bringing down enemy shields. The effectiveness of the shells is poorly understood, and is suspected to lie in the unintended electromagnetic properties of the shell jackets.

text2:
高射炮凶残而有效的双管升级版。以高效撕碎来袭的战机而被冠以：寡妇制造者。

与标准高射炮相同，该武器不仅拥有良好的射速与炮塔转速，且能发射双倍近炸引信炸榴弹并快速歼灭战机与导弹，其环形破片散布也能产生更高的杀伤半径。由于惧怕这种武器的防空能力，而导致战机很少对装有该武器的战舰发动袭击。
text1_095:
An upgraded, viciously effective dual mount of the Flak Cannon. Nicknamed "The Widowmaker" for its ability to tear apart incoming fighters.

Just like the standard flak cannon, this weapon devastates smaller fighter and missile targets, firing two proximity fuse fitted rounds. Shaped dispersal ensures dual detonation and a higher kill radius. Fighter craft are rarely launched against ships that are fitted with this weapon system, out of fear of what it can do. Excellent rate of fire and turret turn rate.
text1_091:

text2:
由{GA-X}工业集团所生产的{Mk.II}突击链炮擅长近距离交火，特别是当精度不如火力密度和射速重要的时候。

拥有电动供弹/退壳系统和集成在炮管内的纳米冷却单元的突击链炮，能以将近每分{400}发的速度向目标倾泻锥形高爆破甲弹，而成为了'肉搏型'舰长们的最爱。

唯一的缺点是武器转速比预想得要慢。这是由于附属的调速器蓝图已经失传，而导致它不得不安装在一些不兼容的转轴上所导致的。
text1_095:
The GA-X Industries Mk. II chaingun excels at close-range fighting, where accuracy is less important than overall damage and volume of fire.

A 'melee' captain's favorite tool, the Assault Chaingun delivers high-explosive shaped charge rounds on target at nearly 400 shells per minute. Features electrically driven feed and ejector systems and an advanced nano cooling unit built right into the barrel. 

The only drawback is a heavier turret profile which, coupled with the lack of the accompanying governor blueprint, is typically mounted on incompatible rotators giving rise to unexpectedly low turret rotation speeds.
text1_091:

The only drawback is a heavier turret profile which, coupled with the lack of the accompanying governor blueprint, is typically mounted on incompatible rotators giving rise to unexpectedly low turret rotation speeds.

text2:
旨在远程破坏装甲的先进武器系统。尽管射速较低但单发伤害较高。

重型撕裂者是一种设计用于攻击中远程目标的残暴武器。它的核心是一门拥有纳米冷却系统和额外散抛壳口的自动加农炮。不过与普通的加农炮所不同的是，重型撕裂者拥有一个能将痕量反物质从标准星舰燃料馈送至炮管的装置。

离开炮膛时，每发炮弹的弹尖都被充入反质子。反质子由重子镀层稳定，并悬浮在炮弹前{10-20}纳米外。当炮弹击中敌舰时，这层反质子'外鞘'会失去稳态并发生质量溃灭，来进一步破坏目标。溃灭反应加上炮弹本身所产生的巨大破坏力而一起作用时，这便使其在对付装甲时尤为有效。
text1_095:
An advanced weapon system designed to punch through armor plating at long-range. Has a low rate of fire and high per-shot damage.

A brutal weapon, the heavy mauler is designed to engage targets at medium to long-range. At its core, the weapon is an autocannon with a nano-cooling system and an external ejection port. However, unlike normal autocannons, the heavy mauler is distinguished by an antimatter barrel charger fed by trivial amounts of standard starship fuel.

When leaving the firing chamber, each shell ogive is charged with a field of antiprotons which hovers 10-20 nanometers in front of the shell, stabilized by a baryon coating. On impact with a target, this antiproton "sheath" loses structural integrity and the resulting reaction does further damage. Given the fact that shells already deliver impressive destructive force to the target, the combined reaction makes the heavy mauler particularly effective versus armored targets.

text2:
使用标准炮弹向中距离目标三发点射的三管自动加农炮。用来对付护盾时最为有效。

这种中口径三联装自动加农炮，不仅采用等口径的标准弹药，且使用的电发火引信也能确保它能准确依次开火。作为一种优秀的火力支援武器，常常被安装于驱逐舰和巡洋舰上，而数组重型自动炮阵列配合恰当的攻击策略甚至能对主力舰构成重大威胁。

但复杂的自动装填机与冷却系统所增加的质量使得炮台的转速相当之慢。
text1_095:
A triple-barreled cannon that fires a burst of standardized shells at medium range. It is most effective versus enemy shields.

Medium caliber, triple-barreled autocannon, typically deployed with medium-bore ammunition. Electrically primed firing fuses ensure precise fire counts. A great fire support weapon, it is typically fitted on destroyer and cruiser class ships. A battery of heavy autocannons with a proper firing solution may pose a serious threat to capital ships. 

Additional mass necessity to accommodate the complex autoloader and cooling systems results in a very poor turn rate.

text1_091cn:
使用标准炮弹向中距离目标三发点射的三管自动加农炮。用来对付护盾时最为有效。

这种中口径三联装自动加农炮，不仅采用等口径的标准弹药，且使用的电发火引信也能确保它能准确依次开火。作为一种优秀的火力支援武器，常常被安装于驱逐舰和巡洋舰上，而数组重型自动炮阵列配合恰当的攻击策略甚至能对主力舰构成重大威胁。

但复杂的自动装填机与冷却系统所增加的质量使得炮台的转速相当之慢。

text2:
用于在远距离内过载并瘫痪敌舰系统的专用武器。所发射的高速硬铀合金块也能有效对付护盾。

高速打击者通过二阶段加速将含有磁性钴铁核心的硬铀合金块加速到极高速度。第一阶段使用化学推进剂加速。并由二阶段磁力线圈进一步加速弹头并稳定弹道。弹头在击中目标前将携带大量电荷，因此在碰撞时会对敌舰产生强大的电磁干扰。
text1_095:
A specialized weapon designed to overload and disable enemy systems from afar. The high-velocity duranium slug is also effective against shields.

The hypervelocity driver uses a 2-stage process to accelerate a duranium slug with a magnetized iron-cobalt core to a very high velocity. A chemical charge accelerates the slug first, then the magnetic coils take over, accelerating the slug further and stabilizing its flight. The slug is highly charged by the time it reaches the target, generating a significant amount of electromagnetic interference on the ship it impacts.

text2:
装在加重底座上的联装轻型针刺。以迅速击溃护盾而被人们所熟知。

在轻型针刺的基础上进行改进后的一种发射小型箭头弹的先进武器，不仅升级了供弹与冷却系统，来进一步提高它的射速，且弹药与前者同样采用了高硬度钨包被的无壳箭弹。
text1_095:
A dual-mount of the Light Needler with a heavier base, this advanced weapon system is capable of quickly overwhelming shield projectors.

The Heavy Needler is an advanced weapon that fires small flechette rounds. An improvement upon the Light Needler, it features better feed and cooling systems, which enable an even greater rate of fire. Projectiles are identical to the light version: caseless ammunition tungsten-jacketed flechettes.
text1_091:

text2:
旨在远程过载目标护盾,所发射的重金属块只能被最厚的装甲挡下。

使用磁力线圈将一枚{300}mm}的超重元素金属块加速到相对论速度。线圈的额定电流通常为几十亿安培,但有时也会超过一万亿安培。与大多数射弹武器不同，高斯炮在开火时会产生大量幅能。且装载该系统的炮塔转向速度也非常缓慢。

尽管非常有效，但实用性却仍被拥有大型实弹接口的典型舰船，低下的反应堆输出功率所限制。
text1_095:
A long-range weapon designed to overload the target's shields. The heavy kinetic slug it fires is also effective against all but the heaviest armor.

Uses magnetic coils to accelerate a 300mm caseless ultra-heavy elemental slug to relativistic speeds. Usually rated at the hundreds of giga-amperes range, rarely exceeding one tera-ampere. Unlike most ballistic weapons, has a very high flux load when fired. Turrets mounted with this system have an extremely poor turn rate. 

Very effective weapon whose usefulness is limited by the low reactor power of ships that typically feature large ballistic weapon mounts.

text2:
旨在用于击穿重甲的中程火炮。其粗野的压制火力也能一并击溃较弱的护盾发生器。

因极具毁灭性而被冠以上古火山之神的名号。其典型的重型炮塔内安装有两门{L/89}型号的炮管，并能以{240}每分的射速来发射高爆破甲弹。而电磁退壳机、电动供弹器以及纳米制冷系统的存在，确保了它能持续开火很长一段时间。而这些低初速的锥形弹头也具备极佳的穿透力。
text1_095:
A medium-range gun designed to punch through heavy armor. The raw damage output also enables it to overwhelm weaker shield emitters.

A truly devastating weapon platform, named for an archaic god of volcanoes. A typical turret mount features two L/89 barrels that trade off firing armor-destroying rounds at 240 RPM. An electromagnetic ejector, powered feed system and nanocoolants allow the weapon to fire for extended time periods. The shaped charge shells have low muzzle velocity and great armor penetrating power.

text2:
强大的中程自动加农炮，能有效对付护盾，也能利用大口径炮弹一并摧毁装甲薄弱的舰体。

众所周知，人之领}早期的战舰并不具备与现代水平相当的装甲保护。而{Mk.IX}型自动炮大概是从{人之领}最早的武器学院设计中得到的改良物。而构成了该武器系统的核心构建则是与两根炮管连接的独特双重供弹系统。

据传，Mk.IX}自动炮的蓝图最早是在英仙座星区某处的恒星重力内的废弃物中所寻获的,不幸的是,一名糟糕的无证估价师在草草看了它一眼之后就宣布该设计过时且无用。之后这份蓝图就被拍卖给了{Ko}联合实业}旗下的一个名叫'自由之星联盟'的小型雇佣军组织，并逐渐淡出人们的视野。

约数个星历年后，自由之星联盟终于制造出第一门原型炮并开始进行武器测试，但该武器在当时来说体积实在过于庞大，不仅只能安装在最大的舰船上，且对装甲的破坏力也比较有限，而射程也并不突出。尽管如此，Mk.IX}自动炮仍用其强悍的攻击力顽强地顶住了那些空谈者的诋毁。并在第二次测试中所展现出的对护盾压倒性的破坏力，而让反对者们彻底闭嘴。

由于这项测试结果未能保密太久，且随处可见的设计蓝图让{Mk.IX}自动炮很快就投入大批量生产以满足全星域的需求。
text1_095:
An imposing medium range autocannon, most effective versus shields. Also obliterates unarmored hulls with a large volume of heavy caliber projectiles.

It is known that warships of the early epoch of the Domain lacked contemporary levels of armor protection. A weapon with a name like the Mark IX Autocannon was probably a refinement of the earliest schools of weapons engineering in the Domain. Two barrels combined with a unique double-loader system form the core of the weapon system.

The Mark IX blueprints were first re-discovered in the Sector from a drifting derelict captured in the gravity well of Penelope's Star. After a hasty examination by an unqualified appraiser, the design was declared obsolete. The blueprint was auctioned off to a small mercenary organization known as the Free Star Combine, a militant subsidiary of the Ko Combine, and forgotten. 

Cycles later, the Free Star Combine finally built a prototype and begun weapon trials. The weapon was deemed too huge, difficult to mount in all but the largest craft, mediocre at best versus armored targets, and its range was anything but extraordinary. Nonetheless, the Mark IX stubbornly refused to be explained away by the theorists, as its raw damage output is impressive. These naysayers were quieted even further when secondary trials showed how utterly devastating the Mark IX is to shield generators.

The results of these trials did not remain secret for long, and the availability of the now common blueprints meant that the Mark IX was quickly manufactured to meet the demand in the Sector.

text2:
能持续产生可观伤害，且具备杰出{EMP}破坏力的中程加农炮。

作为一种非常先进的设计，与传统意义上的加农炮不同，雷神炮采用独特的磁重力炮弹发射器，通过给每枚炮弹的微电容充满足够的能量来在局部形成一个史瓦西半径为{1.8}mm}的奇点，而配合内置的重力场则能摧毁周围的一切并释放令人恐惧的电磁脉冲，以使目标武器与系统瘫痪。
text1_095:
A medium range cannon that delivers superior damage over time and also has a significant EMP payload.

A very advanced design, the Mjolnir is technically a magneto-gravitic shell projector, not a standard cannon. The micro capacitors within each shell are able to deliver enough energy to create a small-scale localized singularity. The built-in gravitic lens devastates all nearby matter, and creates the dreaded electromagnetic pulse (EMP) effect, disabling the target's weapons and systems.
text1_091:

text2:
以极小的散布持续倾泻巨量的针刺弹，如同冰雹般呼啸而过的弹幕，将撕裂它前进道路上的一切。

风暴针刺是一种发射小型无壳箭弹的发射系统，由于其散热需求已经达到中型冷却系统的极限，因此无壳弹武器设计师才给该武器加装了主动型纳米冷却系统，以及多根磁化膛线炮管与自动化操作系统。如今这种能不断从弹药库里向炮塔提供弹药的智能化供弹机，让它能在幅能容量充足时进行不间断射击。

其的射程与射速不仅会对敌方护盾造成巨大压力，也能作为临时点防武器来应对威胁。
text1_095:
Fires multitudes of needles in a tight arc, creating a withering hail of projectiles that rip apart anything in their path. 

The Storm Needler is a flechette weapon, which fires caseless small-bore ammunition. Having reached the practical limits of medium sized cooling systems, the designers of caseless weapons blazed a path into the large weapon category with the Storm Needler's advanced nano coolant recyclers, per-barrel magnetized rifling and automated operation. An intelligent autoloader unpacks and loads just the right amount of ammunition from the magazines, allowing for nonstop operation provided adequate flux capacity.

The good range and speed of projectiles put a great strain on enemy shields, and can also be used effectively versus point defense threats.

其的射程与射速不仅会对敌方护盾造成巨大压力，也能作为临时点防武器来应对威胁。

text2:
发射低速等离子充能弹头的重型加农炮。不仅能有效毁灭装甲。也能一并蒸发周围剩下的所有船体结构。

虽拥有令人恐惧的破坏力，但因制造能安全发射巨大成型的高爆弹头的炮管要求的工艺极度复杂，而导致其很少被使用。但该炮弹击中目标船体时，因诺依曼效应而使弹头会推动高温液态金属射流击穿装甲，并蒸发小片区域，造成船体破损，而泄漏的空气与破片也会让重创内部结构。
text1_095:
A huge cannon which fires slow-moving plasma-charged projectiles. Rounds are highly effective versus armor, and obliterate any hull structure left underneath.

A feared weapon platform, rarely deployed due to the complexity involved in manufacturing a built-up barrel that can safely fire enormous high-explosive shaped charge rounds. When such a shell impacts a target, the Neumann effect causes the warhead to propel a jet of molten metal into the target's armor, vaporizing a small area, causing hull breaches, depressurization, and extensive internal damage from the spall.

text2:
威力强大且具备强力引擎的单发非制导鱼雷。

经典的打击武器，每一枚死神鱼雷都是一种拥有装甲和强力推进器并携带触发式核弹头的运载系统。由于人们普遍猜测它的物理学原理应该早已被{人之领}的权威机构列为高度机密。而导致这款破坏力惊人的鱼雷背后的科学原理依旧未知。如今我们所唯一了解的是，仅凭三到四枚未被点防武器拦截的死神鱼雷，就足以毁灭一艘主力舰。
text1_095:
A single unguided torpedo of devastating yield with a powerful on-board engine.

The quintessential strike weapon, a single Reaper torpedo is a large self-propelled, armored, unguided delivery system for an enriched AM-catalyzed nuclear warhead. The science behind the surprisingly compact detonator is poorly understood in the Sector though widely speculated to be based on physics classified as secret by Domain authority. What is known is that three or four of these slipping through PD arcs are enough to destroy even the largest capital ship.

text1_091cn:
威力强大且具备强力引擎的单发非制导鱼雷。

经典的打击武器，每一枚死神鱼雷都是一种拥有装甲和强力推进器并携带触发式核弹头的运载系统。由于人们普遍猜测它的物理学原理应该早已被{人之领}的权威机构列为高度机密。而导致这款破坏力惊人的鱼雷背后的科学原理依旧未知。如今我们所唯一了解的是，仅凭三到四枚未被点防武器拦截的死神鱼雷，就足以毁灭一艘主力舰。

text2:
这种先进的制导鱼雷因弹头载荷较小，所以才配备了先进的制导系统与更多的用于机动系统消耗的燃料。

作为一种长程制导鱼雷，因每个发射架均拥有两枚可依次发射的鱼雷,而让那些喜欢打击武器的舰长们有了更大的选择余地。由于核弹头会产生能干扰制导系统运行的重子干涉，而将弹头内爆炸物替换成体积更小但威力不减的化学炸弹。
text1_095:
A rack of advanced guided torpedoes. The payload is smaller than usual to make room for the advanced guidance package and maneuvering system's reaction mass.

The Atropos torpedo is a large guided torpedo with an extended range. Each rack mounts two torpedoes which can be fired separately, allowing strike captains maximum flexibility. The AM-catalyzed nuclear warhead typically used in torpedo warheads is missing here as baryonic interference from the detonator would foul the guidance systems. It is replaced by a smaller, yet still potent chemical charge.

text2:
善于摧毁或拦截敌方战机的短程导弹发射器。

采用简单的红外制导系统来获得强大的追踪能力，且微型化学推进器也能提供非凡的机动性。因经过数世纪的实战应用而磨砺进化后的目标算法让蜂群导弹能更精确的追踪目标，且从不失手。
text1_095:
A short range guided missile launcher. The missiles are designed to intercept and destroy enemy fighters.

Launches bursts of small missiles. A simple infrared system provides effective tracking while chemical microthrusters provide exceptional maneuverability. Evolutionary targeting algorithms honed over centuries of real-world application allow the missiles to lead the target - they rarely miss and are very hard to avoid.

text2:
能一次性发射大量且覆盖面积较广的非制导火箭。通常用于敌舰护盾下线时的间隙来借势撕裂目标装甲。

这种小型发射舱通过在一轮齐射中以极短的间隔发射五枚中远程火箭弹，以提高命中率。因火箭体积小且无制导系统，因此额外的空间则被更大的弹头、改进的推进系统以及更厚的装甲所占据。

因多发火箭齐射命中率很高，所以在对付大型目标时表现良好。而在鱼雷攻击前，往往通过利用一轮火箭齐射来吸引点防系统，来为之后的打击火力提供掩护。值得注意的是，歼灭者火箭炮在齐射之后需花费数秒时间来重新装填。
text1_095:
Fires a spread of unguided rockets that cover a wide arc. Typically used to strip away enemy armor once shields are down.

Medium to long-range rockets launched from a small pod that fires five missiles per salvo in a narrow spread to improve the odds of hitting. Rockets are small and unguided, with the extra space being taken up by a larger warhead and improved propulsion systems, as well as thicker armor. 

Performs well against larger targets due to the higher chance of striking with multiple rockets. A rocket attack is often used as a screen before a torpedo strike to reduce the effectiveness of Point Defense systems. Takes several seconds to reload after a salvo.

text2:
能发射一连串的非制导火箭，不仅能有效打击目标装甲，且由于不会产生幅能，使它能持续给敌方施加压制火力。

歼灭者火箭发射器使用与小型发射舱同样的火箭弹，因火箭体积小且无制导系统，因此额外的空间则被更大的弹头、改进的推进系统以及更厚的装甲所占据。

text1_095:
Fires a stream of unguided rockets. Useful for dealing with enemy armor, or - due to having no flux cost - applying sustained pressure.

Features the same medium to long-range rockets found on smaller launchers. Rockets are unguided, with the extra space being taken up by a larger warhead and improved propulsion systems, as well as thicker armor. 

Performs well against larger targets due to the higher chance of striking with multiple rockets. A rocket attack is often used as a screen before a torpedo strike to reduce the effectiveness of Point Defense systems.

text2:
专注锁定目标引擎并试图以强大的电磁脉冲将其瘫痪。其配备的自动装填系统，使它能在拉锯战中发挥出更大的作用。

火蛇导弹是一种拥有两种设计考虑的特殊武器，其一是先进的猎歼机制可以轻松锁定敌舰引擎，同时也能主动规避点防御武器等潜在威胁。

其次是火蛇所用的特殊弹头，与单纯用于摧毁目标的动能或高爆弹头不同，该弹头通过激发强大的定向电磁场，尤其是在没有护盾保护的引擎或船体组件旁爆发时，即可将其电子设备瞬间瘫痪，并使目标被修复前动弹不得。
text1_095:
Homes in on the target's engines and disables them with a powerful EMP burst. A combat-rated autoloader system ensures usefulness in protracted engagements.

The Salamander missile is a specialized weapon with two design considerations. The first is an extremely advanced tracking/targeting mechanism which enables it to home in on enemy engines, whilst avoiding all other potential impact points and Point Defense threats. 

The second is a special warhead design which, instead of attempting to destroy the target with kinetic or explosive force, generates targeted electromagnetic fields of high magnitude. When such a field is created in the proximity of unshielded engines and hull components, it will quickly knock out all their electronics, rendering them useless until repaired.

text2:
发射大当量中程导弹的发射装置。旨在摧毁失去护盾保护的舰船。

这种三联装发射架所搭载的鱼叉导弹，因其先进的推进系统而使一枚大型弹头能以亚光速击中敌舰。以牺牲机动性为代价而换取更高的速度与更大的弹头，而使它成为了星域中应用最为广泛的非打击型武器之一。其卓越的破坏力仅凭一发就足以给护卫舰造成致命打击。

该发射架上装载有数枚鱼叉导弹。
text1_095:
Medium range, high payload guided missile rack. Devastating against ships with downed shields.

Three-racked medium range missiles. An excellent propulsion system delivers a large warhead to the target at sublight speeds. Sacrificing maneuverability for speed and warhead size, the medium range missile is one of the highest yield non strike weapons employed in the Sector. One hit is almost fatal to frigate-sized ships.

This weapon system features a firing rack that houses multiple missiles.

text1_095:
Medium range, high payload guided missile pod. Devastating against ships with downed shields.

An externally mounted pod replaces the more common missile racks and allows multiple missiles to be fired almost simultaneously. An autoloader extracts, arms and primes the next salvo of missiles after a short wait.

These medium range missiles are identical to the ones fired from single or triple racks, and are a great way to finish off a ship with downed shields. An excellent propulsion system delivers a large warhead to the target at sublight speeds. Sacrificing maneuverability for speed and warhead size, the medium range missile is one of the highest yield non strike weapons employed in the sector. One hit is almost fatal to frigate-sized ships.

Medium range, high payload guided missile pod. Devastating against ships with downed shields.

An externally mounted pod replaces the more common missile racks and allows multiple missiles to be fired almost simultaneously. An autoloader extracts, arms and primes the next salvo of missiles after a short wait.

These medium range missiles are identical to the ones fired from single or triple racks, and are a great way to finish off a ship with downed shields. An excellent propulsion system delivers a large warhead to the target at sublight speeds. Sacrificing maneuverability for speed and warhead size, the medium range missile is one of the highest yield non strike weapons employed in the sector. One hit is almost fatal to frigate-sized ships.
text1_091cn:
发射大当量中程导弹的发射装置。旨在摧毁失去护盾保护的舰船。

通过以一种外挂发射架代替了常见的发射系统，而使其能在短时间内连续发射两枚导弹。内置的自动供弹系统也会在短暂等待后开始重新装填，来为下一轮齐射做好准备。

与三联装发射架所搭载的鱼叉导弹相同，因其先进的推进系统而使一枚大型弹头能以亚光速击中敌舰。以牺牲机动性为代价而换取更高的速度与更大的弹头，而使它成为了星域中应用最为广泛的非打击型武器之一。其卓越的破坏力不仅能轻松摧毁护盾下线的战舰,且仅凭一发就足以给护卫舰造成致命打击。

text2:
发射大当量中程导弹的发射装置。旨在摧毁失去护盾保护的舰船。

这个发射架仅携带一枚导弹。

text2:
能以二阶段推进的方式发射一大簇高速动能穿刺弹头，这些弹头不仅能极大地削弱护盾，在击中船体时也能产生不俗的{EMP}伤害。最致命的是，普通点防武器对赛博来说几乎毫无作用。

作为近程二级动能武器。当一级制导导弹携带着二级动能弹头到达攻击距离时，内置计算机将会顺势点燃动能弹头的推进器，正如其名，赛博所使用的二级弹头是由贫铀之类的高密度金属所制成的尾翼稳定脱壳穿甲弹。

虽非常适合用于打击敌舰护盾并使其反应堆超载，但由于如今的标准装甲均有间隔,如果目标及时关闭护盾并以这些致密的装甲来承受穿刺弹头的打击时，其造成的破坏力将大幅降低。

该武器系统装载有数枚赛博导弹。
text1_095:
Fires a 2nd-stage spread of high-velocity kinetic penetrators when in range. Heavy damage to shields, and massive EMP damage when impacting on enemy hull or armor. Difficult to stop with PD.

Sabot-class class missiles are short-range, two-stage KE weapons. A guided missile first stage projects a secondary assembly to within striking distance of a shielded target. The on-board targeting computer then ignites the propellant for a KE penetrator. This 'sabot', as it is commonly called, is typically a narrow, laterally stabilized projectile manufactured from an ultra dense material such as depleted uranium.

Excellent at bringing down enemy shields and causing an overload. Standard ship armor is spaced and thus the sabot deals more manageable damage if shields are lowered in time to receive the impact on armor.

This weapon system features a firing rack that houses multiple missiles.

text2:
适用于给后方作战舰艇提供远程火力支援的大型导弹。其配备的自动装填系统，使它能在拉锯战中发挥出更大的作用。

作为一种技术成熟的武器系统，短矛导弹显然是那些谨慎舰长们进行远程打击的首选。其制导系统虽效率不高但足以威胁到缓慢的大型舰船，不幸的是，这些战舰通常都配备了最好的点防武器，而极大地限制了短矛的作用。
text1_095:
A large guided missile suited for long-range support by backline combat ships. A combat-rated autoloader system ensures continued usefulness in protracted engagements.

A technologically mature weapon system, the Pilum-class missile is the obvious choice for long-range strikes by cautious captains. The guidance system on this weapon make it dangerous versus only the heavier of enemy craft. Unfortunately, those craft also tend to have the best point defense system, which somewhat limits the Pilum's otherwise considerable punch.

text2:
能逐一发射两枚死神鱼雷的双管发射器。可对那些机动性较差的战舰予以毁灭性打击。

这种庞大的武器系统由两根鱼雷发射管与一个能容纳20枚鱼雷的大型弹药库组成。依靠其火控系统,而使其可在一轮内逐一发射两枚死神鱼雷，之后自动填弹装置将在数秒内重装完毕。
text1_095:
Dual launcher system capable of launching a torpedo barrage. Devastating to slow ships that can't move out of the way in time.

A very large weapon system, the Cyclone-class launcher is listed as having two large torpedo tubes with an internal magazine that carries twenty Reaper torpedoes. The fire control system is linked, and fires two Reaper-class torpedoes in tandem. An automatic loader prepares the next salvo from the magazine in seconds.

text2:
能发射在接近目标时分裂成多个小型高爆弹头的导弹。可轻松重创那些失去护盾保护的大型舰船。

飓风{MIRV}发射系统是扩展纪元所设计出的先进武器，旨在发射一种能投射多枚小型高爆制导弹头的动力运载舱。这些拥有锥形装药的小导弹不仅能有效破坏装甲，其内置的弹道计算机可确保所有弹头均可命中目标，且破坏力也足以威胁所有类型的舰船。而整合这些特点的飓风导弹使其成为了战场上闻风丧胆的杀戮利器，而炮手只会在接到彻底摧毁目标的命令时才会发射飓风{MIRV。
text1_095:
Launches a missile that splits into multiple warheads on closing with the target. Especially devastating to enemies with their shields down.

Hurricane Turrets are a late-Expansion Epoch weapon designed to launch a self-propelled, multiple missile delivery projector pod. A targeting computer programs the pod with a hit solution as it is released. The swarm of small missiles released is dangerous to all ship types. missiles feature a shaped charge warhead making them more effective versus enemy armor. These characteristics make the Hurricane a kill-weapon, usually only fired by gunnery officers with orders to destroy their crippled targets utterly.

text2:
用于拦截导弹与战机的一种廉价且实用的激光武器。与众不同的构造使它拥有比大多数点防武器更优秀的射程。

Mk.I}钻探激光炮为了适应战斗，而进行了氟气增益介质改装，且原版小行星追踪系统也被改造以跟踪锁定来袭导弹。无论如何，这种仅发射{670}nm}跟踪光束的武器是无法威胁到大型舰船的。
text1_095:
Cheap utility laser that is hardwired for missile and fighter defense. This configuration gives it longer range than most point defense weapons.

A Mk I mining laser features a fluoride gas gain medium refitted for combat. The micro-asteroid targeting package has been repurposed to track and target incoming missiles. Mostly useless for anything larger or armored targets. Has a built-in 670nm tracker beam.
text1_091:

text2:
用于拦截导弹与战机的小型激光武器。以极佳的追踪性能、良好的破坏力以及较短的射程而被人们所熟知。

简单可靠以及低幅能输出使得{PD}激光炮成为了一种应用较为广泛的点防武器。由二氧化碳增益介质与近程标记激光所组成，因这种简单的一级透镜无需移动组件，因此在没有维护程序的情况下也能长时间正常运作。不过较低的伤害使得'希望那是哑弹'的祈祷词被广为人知。
text1_095:
Small laser designed for missile and fighter defense, with great tracking capability, decent damage and very short range.

Simplicity, reliability and low flux costs characterize this ubiquitous point-defense weapon. The laser is built around a carbon dioxide gain medium combined with a short range marker beam. A simple one stage lens assembly with no moving parts permits the weapon to operate for extended periods without maintenance procedures. Low damage has prompted the creation of the "Pray [it's a] Dud" Laser backronym.

text2:
非常灵活的标准战斗激光炮，在中远距离均有不错的表现。但对付无护盾保护的目标时效果最佳。

战术激光是射束武器领域的代表性作品，因其维护成本低、用途广泛且易于制造，而成为了星域激光武器中值得信赖的选择。由一种能发射波长为{670}nm}的标准二氧化碳介质增益激光器与三组透镜组件构成，因此非常适合作为小型战舰上的支援武器，特别是在长期交战中表现最好。
text1_095:
Standard combat laser, useful at medium to long-ranges. A very flexible weapon, especially effective against unshielded targets.

The workhorse of beam weapons in the sector, the tactical laser is often used because of its low maintenance cost, versatility and ease of construction. Features a standard carbon dioxide gain medium, a 670nm marker beam and three lens assemblies. A good support weapon for small craft, especially in prolonged engagements.

text2:
能连续发射电磁脉冲以快速瘫痪敌舰系统与引擎的中程能量炮。命中时还能产生攻击着弹点附近系统的电弧。

离子炮的非标准增益介质能将重子物质在发射器中高度离子化，当离子团击中目标时，将会产生局部电磁场，并将周围包括传感器、燃料点火器、定位模块、计算机在内的所有电子设备带来灭顶之灾。尽管该武器会熔断某些电路，对护盾产生轻微应变，但所造成的永久性伤害几乎可以忽略不计，所以很少有人会在自己的船上装满这些玩意。
text1_095:
A medium range energy cannon that delivers an electromagnetic pulse (EMP) and can quickly disable enemy systems/engines. May arc to modules near the point of impact.

The Ion Cannon's nonstandard gain medium projects highly-ionized baryonic matter in a coherent bolt. When the ion bolt impacts the target it creates a localized magnetic field which plays havoc with all manner of electronics, including sensors, fuel igniters, targeting modules, computers, etc. The weapon also fuses certain circuits, and can mildly strain shield generators, thus it does negligible amount of permanent damage. Rarely the only weapon type fitted on ships.

text1_095: A slow-firing, medium range energy cannon that delivers an electromagnetic pulse (EMP) and can quickly disable enemy systems/engines. May arc to modules near the point of impact.

text2:
幅能效率较高的红外激光脉冲,能长时间发射中程能量束来压制敌舰。

与大多数激光武器相似，IR}脉冲激光采用标准的二氧化碳增益介质来发射{11}微米波段的脉冲束。且持续供给能源的{Q开关}足以支撑到{IR}脉冲把目标熔化，尽管比传统激光炮更为有效，但功耗也会更多。常被应用于战斗机或护卫舰之上，以便利用良好的机动性来弥补其射程上的不足。
text1_095:
A flux-efficient infrared pulse laser which fires bolts of energy at medium range. An excellent weapon for prolonged bursts of fire.

This weapon is identical to most combat lasers with a carbon dioxide gain medium fired at eleven microns. A q-switched power supply permits ablation of the target which makes the weapon much more effective than a conventional beam, at the cost of much higher power consumption. Most often used on fighters or frigates, where the low range of the weapon can be offset by the maneuverability of the fitted craft.

text2:
用于拦截导弹与战机的中程激光武器，虽能长时间开火但威力颇低。

通过加装额外透镜来解决标准二氧化碳激光器在工作时会散射的问题，由于仍发射波长为{11}微米的激光，而导致射程加长的它因较低的输出功率而大大削弱了伤害。其唯一的优势就是可以用来对付赛博这种特殊的反护盾导弹，毕竟标准的点防武器可没有那么远的射程来拦截这些狡猾的家伙。
text1_095:
Medium range energy weapon, effective at neutralizing missile and fighter threats. Can be fired for extended periods, but the damage is subpar.

An additional lens assembly eliminates self-diffusing particles from a standard carbon dioxide beam fired at a wavelength of eleven microns. The extended range permits the otherwise low wattage to have a greater impact on the targets. Particularly useful in destroying missiles headed for a shielded target - a standard point defense laser generally doesn't have the range to extend far enough past the defensive shields of the ship it is supposed to protect.

text2:
拥有内置电容的瞬发{PD}激光炮可在短时间内以极快的速度对目标予以连续打击。只要给予足够的充能时间，它就能成为拦截效率最高的点防武器之一。

由{PD}激光炮改进而来，利用{Q开关}与脉冲泵浦方式，来确保能量按预设的间隔达到峰值时，供给到钛蓝宝石增益介质。其结果就是，这种每隔数秒就能开火一次的武器，在拦截小型目标时效率极佳。且极低的功耗，甚至能让一些战机动力核心也能承受其射击负荷。
text1_095:
Features a built-in capacitor that lets the weapon fire several bursts in quick succession if allowed to fully recharge. Excellent vs missiles and fighters.

The burst point defense laser is a further refinement of standard PD beam weapons. The q-switched gain medium is pulse pumped, ensuring that the power delivered to the titanium-doped sapphire gain medium peaks at a predefined interval. The result is a weapon that fires once every couple of seconds and is extremely effective for its small size. Power consumption is small enough that even some fighter craft power cores can handle the firing load.

text2:
射速极为缓慢但破坏力极高的能量炮，虽射程极短，但足以对星域中最大的战舰构成威胁。

因所发射的反物质需存储至内置有能产生强大磁场的嵌套壳体内，而使其成为了现存武器中最复杂的一种。为了制造一个强大到足以容纳10微克的反物质(通常是正电子)的电磁场，而导致内置的电容必须花费较长时间的充能。一旦产生至少2.5万牛顿约束力的电磁场时，外壳将瞬间破裂，而里面的反物质将会在开火时产生的洛伦茨力的作用下射向目标。
text1_095:
A slow-firing, extremely high damage energy gun meant to pose a threat to the largest ships in the Sector. Can only be used at close-range.

The antimatter blaster is one of the most complicated weapons in existence. Antimatter is stored in shells that have their own powered magnetic field projector built into the casing. In order to generate a field strong enough to contain and eject the antimatter (typically positrons) the built-in capacitor must spend a considerable time charging. Once a magnetic field of the required strength is generated, the shell is breached and the antimatter is ejected toward the target, its main propellant being the Lorentz force around the muzzle of the blaster. 

Extremely effective versus all targets.

text2:
射程与持续时间短，但威力巨大的激光武器，与其他瞬发光束类似，均拥有极佳的装甲破坏力。

利用三倍蓝宝石增益介质，以确保能发射最大波长的激光。此外通过超维滤波器发射的光子，其部分能量也将被转入{P}空间输出。不过由于这套滤波器相关的物理原理尚未被完全理解，因为在实验室测试中，超过6.66吉瓦的光束在{p}空间分量时会随机发生震荡，如同被无形的屏障阻挡一样，因此如今实际使用中的相位长矛不会采取如此之高的能量水平以保证其稳定性。
text1_095:
A short-range, short-duration beam that causes heavy damage in a burst. Capable against armor, as far as beam weapons go.

This weapon is, at base, simply a laser beam with a tripled sapphire gain medium to ensure the highest possible weaponized wavelengths. The photons are fired through a hyperdimensional filter which outputs an energy beam that exists partially in p-space. The physics of the filter are not properly understood, and in laboratory settings the p-space components of a beam exceeding 6.66 giga-watts will sometimes flicker - as if blocked. Weapon mounts never use such high energy levels to ensure reliability.

text2:
能远距离对护盾持续施压的非典型光束武器。但无法威胁到装甲。

基于一种超膜裂隙发生器与波长为{500}nm}的激光追踪器所构成。该光束会给人工操作员提供目标反馈的同时，来为展开局部时空裂隙做好准备。

当空间裂隙被打开，高维宇宙膜中的重力子会大量进入当前时空，并存留约{1}秒左右。而由此产生的引力切变不仅会对目标造成一定伤害，且这种高维度重力子也能有效压制目标能量护盾。
text1_095:
An atypical beam weapon which is highly effective versus shields. Excellent range, but the damage per second ratio vs armor is sub-par.

The core of this weapon is a brane rift generator which follows a 500nm tracer beam. The beam prepares local space-time for the rift in addition to providing targeting feedback to manual operators. 

Once the rift is open, higher-brane gravitons enter local space time en masse and persist up to 100 centiseconds. Damage to the target is caused by the resulting intense gravimetric shear. These higher-brane gravitons easily overwhelm standard energy fields.

text2:
能连续发射能量束的武器，对于拥有足够幅能寄存并希望能在中距交火中持续压制敌人的舰长来说非常有用。

一种发射脉冲激光而非恒定光束，且总输出功率远超前者的设计。但与大部分激光发射器相似的是,它仍采用了二氧化碳增益介质激光器所产生的波长为{11}微米的光子。

短时间内输出更多的能量脉冲激光,将会使目标装甲表层被逐渐烧蚀并最终气化，并由此产生的冲击波也会对船体结构造成一定的损伤。
text1_095:
Fires repeating bolts of energy, favoring the medium-range combatant that has the flux reserves and wants to put constant pressure on the enemy.

Designed to fire pulses rather than a constant beam, with a total power output exceeding constant-operation designs. As with continuous lasers, a carbon dioxide gain medium is fed energy and produces photons at eleven microns wavelengths. 

Greater energy delivered in shorter time means the target is ablated, a process that causes the vaporization of small surfaces sections. The resulting shock waves do additional structural damage.

text2: 钻探冲击波不仅是矿工的好伙伴，且能以大量幅能为代价,向中程目标发射粉碎性的能量束。
text1_095: The miner's best friend, this weapon can deliver pulverizing bolts of energy at medium range, albeit at extreme cost in flux.
text1_091: The miner's best friend, this weapon can deliver pulverizing bolts of energy at medium range, albeit at extreme cost in flux.
text1_091cn: 钻探冲击波不仅是矿工的好伙伴，且能以大量幅能为代价,向中程目标发射粉碎性的能量束。

text2:
能连续发射能量束的武器。极高的破坏力与极高的幅能输出，使其成为最具杀伤性的武器之一。

这种可靠的武器系统，采用了能在强大电流下转变为等离子体的改进型高能气体作为弹药。开火前，一个引导电子会被预先沿着发射轨道，以确保其不稳定的等离子团能以预定的方向前进。而这也得归功于一种不太容易理解的物理特性。
text1_095:
Fires bolts of energy at enemy targets. With high damage and flux costs, the heavy blaster is one of the most damaging weapons for its size.

A reliable energy weapon, the Heavy Blaster uses improved high-energy gas ammunition which, when activated by a strong electric current, is converted into plasma. A guiding electron is fired along the axis of traversal beforehand, ensuring that the uncontained plasma bolt will travel in the intended direction, thanks to physics that are no longer well understood.

text2:
瞬发{PD}激光炮的重型版本，拥有着更优秀的射程与更多的电容器，以大幅提高其拦截效率。

这种常常被低估的武器，其实是星域中性能最好的激光武器之一。哪怕对透镜外壳和增益介质进行粗略测试，就足以使那些最持怀疑态度的检查员也得承认这是{人之领}所能提供的最好技术成果。

无论{霸主}军备委员会的高级研究员，还是{速子科技}高科技研究处的科学家，都不能完全理解它产生脉冲效果的原理。其理论上基于{Q开关}产生的多相位光束，与通过量子滤波器产生的量子纠缠效应。这大概也解释了原本被认为是故障保险系统的三级透镜外壳的作用。不过这仅是理论而已。

在战斗中，重型瞬发激光炮最受那些希望拥有先进点防系统的舰长喜爱。
text1_095:
A heavier version of the PD Burst Laser, this weapon features a longer range and a greater number of built-in capacitors for higher up-front damage.

An often underestimated weapon, the heavy burst laser is actually one of the best performing beam weapons available in the Sector. A cursory examination of the gain medium and lens housing is often enough to assure even the most skeptical inspector that the technology housed within is some of the best the Domain had to offer. 

The physics that create the burst effect are not understood by the highest echelons of the Hegemony Armaments Committee or even the Tri-Tachyon Hybrid Physics Division. It is theorized that a q-switched multi-phased beam could be shot through a quantum filter which would ensure entanglement and create a burst effect. This may be an explanation for the tripled lens housing, originally thought to be a failsafe system. But these are just theories. 

In combat, the Heavy Burst Laser is favored by those that want be assured that their point defense perimeter is state-of-the-art.

text2:
这种巨大而神秘的武器大概是星域中最具破坏力的持续伤害制造者。前提是安装该武器的战舰能处理它所产生的巨额幅能。

与引力子激光以及相位长矛类似，它们均利用了少有记载的薄膜物理学原理来发射它们的载荷。等离子炮所使用的炮弹是一种利用重力透镜和重子透镜向内聚焦能量而形成的微聚变炸弹。而聚焦过程导致的爆炸将产生一团暂时被异常空间控制的等离子团。当这些等离子团在磁场的控制下飞向目标时，仅持续数秒的约束场也会在等离子体到达目标前瓦解，如果这团能量场的凸起外壳未被物质或能量产生{9000}N}的力破坏的话，那么更高一级的膜便会吸收破坏性的等离子体，并使它永远从我们的维度中消失。
text1_095:
A large, arcane weapon that's one of the most devastating sustained damage-dealers in the Sector, provided the ship it's mounted on can handle the flux it generates.

Plasma cannons are related to graviton and phase beams, in that they use poorly-documented properties of brane physics to deliver their payloads. A plasma cannon shell is a microfusion bomb which uses gravitic and baryonic lens to focus its energy inward. The resulting explosion creates plasma which is contained by a temporary mini-universe anomaly, while magnetic drivers mounted on the forward pylons accelerate it toward the target. The containment field lasts only a couple seconds, which is usually long enough for the anomaly to reach a target. If the convex hull of the field is not breached by ordinary matter/energy delivering at least 9 kN, the higher brane will absorb the destructive plasma, and it will vanish from our dimension forever.

text2:
这种射程远伤害高的激光武器，常被安装在那些需要高效反装甲武器的舰船或者火力支援舰上。

高强度激光是一种威力巨大的能量武器，拥有一个能量密度超过千兆瓦级的能量源。为了长时间提供如此巨大的能量，而设计了一个内置的聚变能源核心。尽管如此，该核心依旧需要一套外部的控制系统与在开始攻击时从舰船反应堆提供额外能量的管线。

三组高精度透镜将光子聚焦到点火单元上，并在数秒内充入能量以形成相干光束。高强度激光的增益介质是二阶气-固态物质，它们能形成{Q开关}，并产生使目标在数秒内消失的强大粒子流。

由于极远的锁定距离与射程，使高强度激光能在确保安全的前提下为正在近身鏖战的友军舰船提供密接支援。而那些有能力在使用它的同时控制好幅能的舰长们则很喜爱这个玩意。
text1_095:
A long-range, high damage beam weapon, often mounted on support ships, or ships that need anti-armor capability on a budget.

The High Intensity Laser is a powerhouse weapon that has an energy rating well beyond the giga-watt range. To produce such power for an extended period of time, the design relies on a built-in fusion power core. This core still requires an external actuator, a role filled by a ship's reactor when firing commences. 

Three meticulously calibrated lens assemblies guide photons within the ignition unit, requiring seconds to build up the energy necessary to maintain a coherent beam. The gain medium is a two-staged gas-solid which is q-switched and provides a potent particle stream that can obliterate unsuspecting targets in seconds.

The extreme range at which targets can be tracked and destroyed makes the HIL excel in safely providing close support to friendly ships that are engaged in a melee. It is a favored weapon of captains that can manage the flux cost associated with operating it.

text2: 大量的内置电容是这种极为高效而强大的能量武器的成功秘诀。但较低的持续射击率大大降低了这种消耗累计电荷武器的破坏力。
text1_095: Numerous built-in capacitors are at the core of this extremely efficient, yet potent energy weapon. The high burst damage from expending built-up charges is offset by the comparatively low sustained firing rate.
text1_091: Numerous built-in capacitors are at the core of this extremely efficient, yet potent energy weapon. The high burst damage from expending built-up charges is offset by the comparatively low sustained firing rate.
text1_091cn: 大量的内置电容是这种极为高效而强大的能量武器的成功秘诀。但较低的持续射击率大大降低了这种消耗累计电荷武器的破坏力。

text2:
由装满小型激光炮的旋转吊舱所构成的点防系统，其内置的电容器足以让它以极高的效率拦截来袭的战机与导弹。

拥有侦测并击毁一切突破护航部队火力圈的战机和导弹的军用级点防御武器。因其夸张的体积与较高的幅能输出，使保卫者系统一般只会被安装在主力舰上。

利用自主型亚伽玛AI核心与五组独立二氧化碳激光器组合，且独立的转向系统供能装置使它几乎能瞬间锁定目标。虽较高的能源需求意味着仅能维持数秒开火，但也足以应对绝大多数威胁。
text1_095:
A collection of smaller lasers mounted together on a rotating pod, with a built-in capacitor allowing extremely high burst damage vs fighters and missiles.

The Paladin is a military grade PD system that is usually only deployed on capital ships due to its high production and flux costs. Can detect and destroy incoming strike weapons and enemy fighters that have penetrated the capital ship's defensive escort screen. 

A combination of an autonomous sub-gamma AI core for targeting and five separate carbon dioxide lasers make this weapon exceptionally effective in point defense. A dedicated rotator power supply makes target tracking almost instantaneous. The prohibitive energy requirement usually means that the weapon is only activated for seconds at a time, but that is usually enough to deal with any PD threat.

text2:
作为攻势-级战列舰的主要组成部分，这种笨重的旧型能量武器可以为其提供压倒性的正面火力。

热脉冲加农炮设计于模块化的设计思路被{人之领}海军设计师们普遍接受之前。由于当时根本没有其他舰船能容纳这种巨型武器的空间，或是拥有能满足其能量需求的反应堆，而导致该武器被硬编码进了攻势-级的蓝图当中。

尽管被后来一些模块化武器设计所超越，但该武器依然是攻势-级武器库中不可或缺的一部分。
text1_095:
A bulky energy weapon from an early epoch, the TPC is built directly into the Onslaught's hull and provides overwhelming frontal firepower.

Designed before modular energy weapons were universally trusted by Domain naval architects, this weapon was coded into the Onslaught's blueprint because no other hull of the time was large enough or had reactors capable of generating the requisite power.

Even though it's outperformed by some of the later epoch modular designs, the Thermal Pulse Cannon remains an integral part of the Onslaught's arsenal.

text2:
拥有毁灭性破坏力与{EMP}洪流的瞬发型光束武器。

速子长矛因其强大的威力与极高的稀有度而在星域中有着传奇般的地位。它的核心技术是基于实验性的{FTL}通信系统的原型机，并通过{N}膜控制系统与反等离子体所产生的一种在超空间内流动的带电粒子风暴来打击目标，而非利用超光速粒子的超维特性进行通信。由于该系统所需求的能量极其惊人，而导致即便配备有全星域最大电容器的速子长矛也仅能维持数秒开火。

与普通光束武器发射的光束不同，由于那些超光速粒子没法聚焦或被约束，因为事实上当速子长矛倾尽所有能量激发超光速粒子时，这些粒子就会将射击线上的一切毁灭殆尽，而当如此高能的反等离子体经过普通空间时，它所诱发的电磁风暴、引力位移与热穴效应将撕裂路径上的一切，并同时对附近的电子仪器造成严重的破坏。
text1_095:
A burst operated beam that delivers a devastating amount of damage with a cascading EMP component. The EMP arcs have a chance to pass through shields based on the target's hard flux level.

A weapon so rare and powerful that it has achieved mythical status in the Sector, the Tachyon Lance uses core technology based on the principles of an experimental FTL communication system prototype, but with a twist. Instead of using the hyperdimensional properties of the tachyon particle for communication, n-brane manipulation and anti-plasma generators create a charged tachyon stream that travels in hyperspace. Minimum energy requirements are staggering and this amount of power can only be generated for a few seconds by the largest power capacitors, which are housed within the weapon system. 

Unlike the beams fired from normal beam weapons, the tachyon stream is not lensed or altered in any way - in fact once the initial tachyon marker is actuated the reaction takes on a life of its own, rapidly consuming the power stored in the capacitors and unleashing destruction. When normal space is exposed to such high levels of anti-plasma, a combined electromagnetic, gravitic and thermal cavitation effect shreds anything that stands in its way, while also severely damaging nearby electronics equipment.
text1_091:
A burst operated beam that delivers a devastating amount of damage with a cascading EMP component. The EMP arcs have a chance to pass through shields based on the target's hard flux level.

A weapon so rare and powerful that it has achieved mythical status in the Sector, the Tachyon Lance uses core technology based on the principles of an experimental FTL communication system prototype, but with a twist. Instead of using the hyperdimensional properties of the tachyon particle for communication, n-brane manipulation and anti-plasma generators create a charged tachyon stream that travels in hyperspace. Minimum energy requirements are staggering and this amount of power can only be generated for a few seconds by the largest power capacitors, which are housed within the weapon system. 

Unlike the beams fired from normal beam weapons, the tachyon stream is not lensed or altered in any way - in fact once the initial tachyon marker is actuated the reaction takes on a life of its own, rapidly consuming the power stored in the capacitors and unleashing destruction. text1_091cn:
拥有毁灭性破坏力与{EMP}洪流的瞬发型光束武器。

速子长矛因其强大的威力与极高的稀有度而在星域中有着传奇般的地位。它的核心技术是基于实验性的{FTL}通信系统的原型机，并通过{N}膜控制系统与反等离子体所产生的一种在超空间内流动的带电粒子风暴来打击目标，而非利用超光速粒子的超维特性进行通信。由于该系统所需求的能量极其惊人，而导致即便配备有全星域最大电容器的速子长矛也仅能维持数秒开火。

与普通光束武器发射的光束不同，由于那些超光速粒子没法聚焦或被约束，因为事实上当速子长矛倾尽所有能量激发超光速粒子时，这些粒子就会将射击线上的一切毁灭殆尽，而当如此高能的反等离子体经过普通空间时，它所诱发的电磁风暴、引力位移与热穴效应将撕裂路径上的一切，并同时对附近的电子仪器造成严重的破坏。

text2:
历史悠久的著名设计。在包括先进打击武器、能量武器、护盾系统均未被开发出的远古时期，攻势-级战列舰就已经开始服役于{人之领}中的无敌舰队。

当攻势-级第一次从轨道船坞发射升空时，这艘让周遭舰船相形见绌的庞然大物让整片星域都为之震颤。甚至有传言称它们是在一场早已被遗忘的战争中被制造出来用以对抗异族的中流砥柱。后来，人之领}的工程师对其蓝图进行了全方位改进，不仅增加了护盾系统、升级了超光速引擎、还通过自动化和迭代工程减少了必要船员的数量。即使有其它更先进的主力舰蓝图，但由于系统极其简单，因此攻势-级仍然是当今最容易生产的主力舰之一。

这艘在设计时就未曾考虑护盾的战舰仅凭可靠装甲就能在承受猛烈炮火的同时,最大程度保护船员们的安全并组织有效反击，因而深受军官和船员们的爱戴。尽管在后勤方面需依赖大量的弹药补给，但凭借其无与伦比的正面火力，让攻势-级可在数分钟内摧毁整支舰队。

如今，攻势-级以中坚力量的角色，骄傲地服役于{霸主}无敌舰队之中。
text1_095:
A venerable design, the Onslaught-class battleships were first created to serve the Domain Armada long ago, before the development of advanced strike weapons, modern energy weapons, and shield systems. 

When first launched from orbital dock, they must have surely dwarfed any other ship in existence and intimidated entire systems. Some even say that they were built to combat non-humans in a long forgotten war. Much later, Domain engineers made modifications to the blueprints to include a shield system, upgraded the FTL drives, and reduced the necessary crew complement through automation and iterative engineering. Even though more advanced blueprints are available, the Onslaught remains the easiest to manufacture due to the brutal simplicity of its systems. 

A ship designed without shields in mind, built to be able to withstand a heavy barrage of enemy fire and strike back while protecting its crew is much loved by its officers and crew. And strike back it can; the Onslaught's unmatched ballistic potential can devastate entire fleets in minutes, its only drawback a logistical dependency on ammunition. 

The Onslaught-class proudly serves as the backbone of the Hegemony Navy.

text2:
技术先进的主力舰，星体-级航母通过所搭载的大量战机联队来为其提供强大的火力输出。

在'大崩塌'前几年里，星体-级一直被公认是航母设计领域中的缩影。除部分点防武器和导弹发射架外，该舰几乎所有的自动化系统以及防御模块都是由复杂的{(但未过于复杂的){AI}系统来进行操控。

星体-级的主要火力通常都依赖所搭载的战机联队，由于这些数量庞大的战机具备极为灵活的战术空间，因此只要敌舰出现在有效打击范围内，就可用一个简单的起飞命令，借助敏捷的截击机、轰炸机、战斗机将其快速粉碎，且高度自动化的整备设施能确保从战斗中返航的舰载机能快速维修或重新武装。尽管该航母能借助强大的{X-35}护盾来确保自身安全，可一旦护盾发生器离线，那么它将变得异常脆弱，因此星体-级一般处于星载航母舰队中的前锋位置，而绝不会在没有战机联队保护的情况下独自航行。但即便是在如今，人们依旧很难在庞大的星域中遇见这些特种舰队，原因在于除了征服整颗行星或者封锁大片宇宙空间以外，就没有什么任务需要如此强大的武力。

目前，这艘在已知星域中最先进的航母由于复杂的构造对轨道船坞的生产技术要求非常严格，因此鲜有星体-级服役于{霸主}舰队之中。且仅有速子旗下的高级军官或某位极其富有的海军上将，才会偶尔建造一艘星体-级并作为旗舰来使用。
text1_095:
A technologically advanced capital ship designed primarily as a carrier, the Astral-class is able to project vast amounts of firepower through its numerous fighter craft squadrons.

The Astral-class ships are thought to have been the epitome of carrier design in the Domain during the years prior to the Collapse. Nearly all systems that can be automated are, with each handled by sophisticated (but not too sophisticated) sub-AI cores installed throughout the ship. Defensive weapon systems are typically, but not always, point defense turrets and long-range missiles. 

The true power of an Astral lies in its fighter craft, which give the carrier unprecedented flexibility in the battle space. Nearly any enemy ship type that appears on the captain's scopes can quickly be dispatched, given just a launch order of a wing of nimble interceptors, strike bombers or fighters. Automated facilities ensure that a squadron coming back from a mission can quickly be repaired and rearmed behind the safety of the powerful X-35 shield emitter. The Astral-class is very vulnerable should the X-35 come down. This is why when not protected by its fighter wings it never travels alone, but instead is at the head of space-borne carrier fleets. These task forces are a rarity, as the power they hold is usually required to subjugate entire planets or blockade enormous areas of space.

The Astral is perhaps the most technologically advanced capital ship that can be seen in the Sector today. Few serve with the Hegemony due to the high technological requirements that it imposes on orbital docks. Senior Naval Corporate Officers of the Tri-Tachyon Corporation or extremely wealthy private admirals sometimes make an Astral their flagship.

text2:
可轻易装载成百上千单位的集装箱，且配有超光速引擎和少量防御系统的星载货运平台。

旨在为偏远的前哨站点提供全面的充足补给，因此阿特拉斯-级不适合本星域中最普遍的小量、快捷的贸易活动。由于其庞大的体积与缓慢的速度，导致它出现的地方经常会吸引一些不请自来的'客人'，从充满好奇心的围观群众，到一心想破坏集装箱磁重力固定器的海盗，甚至还有想彻底摧毁它的狂信徒。尽管如此，阿特拉斯-级依旧被{霸主}广泛应用于多项重要运输任务中，尤其是因季节而需大量运输的农业产物。为此{霸主}专门组建起了一支由阿特拉斯-级为主的庞大运输队，并用大量全副武装的巡洋舰充当护航编队，以此确保{霸主}人民的生命线不被切断。

被任命为阿特拉斯-级的船长，大概是对能人的一种罕见惩罚，同时航行过程中所充满着的厌倦与恐惧，分别是例行货运和海盗袭击时的产物。
text1_095:
The Atlas-class ships are large space-borne cargo platforms with an FTL drive and a few defensive systems. Hundreds of containers can be latched on to the hull and carried with ease by this behemoth. 

Typically used to efficiently resupply entire outposts, the Atlas is ill suited to the small and fast trade runs that are the mainstay of commerce in the sector. Their slow speed and large size always tempt uninvited guests, ranging from curious gawkers come to see the hulking colossus, to scavenging pirates aiming to disable a container's magneto-gravitic fastener, to Pather fanatics bent on destroying it all. Nonetheless, the Hegemony makes wide use of them, especially to offload biomass from farming worlds on a seasonal basis. For this purpose, the Hegemony assembles large Atlas convoys; these are protected by military cruisers that ensure that the lifeline of Hegemony citizens is kept safe.

The captaincy of an Atlas is a rare punishment for the able, an uneven mixture of soul-numbing boredom and abject terror, being the results of normal trade runs and pirate attacks, respectively.

text1_091cn:
可轻易装载成百上千单位的集装箱，且配有超光速引擎和少量防御系统的星载货运平台。

旨在为偏远的前哨站点提供全面的充足补给，因此阿特拉斯-级不适合本星域中最普遍的小量、快捷的贸易活动。由于其庞大的体积与缓慢的速度，导致它出现的地方经常会吸引一些不请自来的'客人'，从充满好奇心的围观群众，到一心想破坏集装箱磁重力固定器的海盗，甚至还有想彻底摧毁它的狂信徒。尽管如此，阿特拉斯-级依旧被{霸主}广泛应用于多项重要运输任务中，尤其是因季节而需大量运输的农业产物。为此{霸主}专门组建起了一支由阿特拉斯-级为主的庞大运输队，并用大量全副武装的巡洋舰充当护航编队，以此确保{霸主}人民的生命线不被切断。

被任命为阿特拉斯-级的船长，大概是对能人的一种罕见惩罚，同时航行过程中所充满着的厌倦与恐惧，分别是例行货运和海盗袭击时的产物。

text2:
征服者-级战列巡洋舰是集中火力理念的具象化产物。因它在战机还未大范围普及的时间点面世,所以该战舰选择了通过削弱装甲厚度来强调火力以及速度。

那时太空海军战术家们深信，新的武器系统总是会胜过装甲与护盾，也是取得一场战斗胜利的关键因素。那么为什么不建造一艘专注于速度与火力的战舰呢？仅配以巡洋级别的防护,但赋予其所能用的最强武器,并确保速度上能超过配有同级武器的其它巨舰,显然征服者-级就是综合了这一切理念的杰作。除此之外,许多先进技术也被纳入该设计之中，其中就包括了拥有高效作战设计的圆形武器底座。尽管较高的机动水平意味着需配合更好的好航行技能，但却能为指挥官提供更多的战术选择。

古语云：'勇者天佑'征服者-级的确眷顾着那些勇敢的舰长，那些不惜一切代价渴求胜利的人们。
text1_095:
The Conquest-class battlecruiser is the embodiment of concentrated firepower. Developed in the period just preceding the popularization of fighter craft, the class emphasizes firepower and speed over armor protection.

Space Naval tacticians of the day were confident that new weapons systems would always outperform armor and shields and thus were the key to winning an engagement. So why not build a ship for speed and power? Give it the armor protection of a cruiser, but arm it with the best weapons available to any ship, and have it remain faster than any of those lumbering behemoths of the line. The Conquest is a good example of these concepts put into a hull. Many other advanced technologies were incorporated into the design, including weapon mounts designed for a circling engagement. This maneuver requires greater navigational skill while serving to provide more tactical options to the commanding officers. 

Fortune favors the bold, the ancients said. This class of ships does indeed favor the bold captain, willing to risk everything for the thrill of victory.

text2:
人之领}战舰设计中的巅峰之作，不仅仅是军事上的必要性而造就了该主力舰的诞生，更多的是海军部某些高层军官的野心在{速子科技}以及主要承包商的大力支持下所带来的结果。

没有任何一艘主力舰要比典范-级更加坚挺、强大，它是旧时代真正意义上的无敌巨舰。
text1_095:
The pinnacle of the Domain's battleship designs, though perhaps less the result of military necessity and more of the ambitions of certain senior strategic staff of the Domain Navy - with considerable backing from the Tri-Tachyon corporation, among other major contractors.

No ship can outlast or outgun the Paragon-class, a true Leviathan of a bygone epoch.
text1_091:

text1_091cn:
人之领}战舰设计中的巅峰之作，不仅仅是军事上的必要性而造就了该主力舰的诞生，更多的是海军部某些高层军官的野心在{速子科技}以及主要承包商的大力支持下所带来的结果。

没有任何一艘主力舰要比典范-级更加坚挺、强大，它是旧时代真正意义上的无敌巨舰。

text2: 尽管不对称的球形设计掩盖了这艘战列巡洋舰的真正实力，但凭借独特的船体构造与战术系统,使奥德赛-级不仅将能量武器与机动战术完美衔接，同时内置的飞行甲板也提供了更多的战术选择。
text1_095: The asymmetric, spheroid design belies the power of this battlecruiser. The base hull presents a tactical setup that favors energy weapons and mobility. Carrier capabilities further augment its tactical options.
text1_091: The asymmetric, spheroid design belies the power of this battlecruiser. The base hull presents a tactical setup that favors energy weapons and mobility. Carrier capabilities further augment its tactical options.
text1_091cn: 尽管不对称的球形设计掩盖了这艘战列巡洋舰的真正实力，但凭借独特的船体构造与战术系统,使奥德赛-级不仅将能量武器与机动战术完美衔接，同时内置的飞行甲板也提供了更多的战术选择。

text2:
笨重但极具威胁，统治者-级是{霸主}领域内，被广泛应用的星系防御巡洋舰之一。

尽管不是最先进的船体构造，但统治者-级凭借所配备的大量实弹武器挂载点，来轻松完成保卫固定设施和关键贸易商路的使命。但由于它的护盾性能低下且难以管理，因此使该舰更注重于利用重型装甲来抵御大多数猛烈炮火。除了坚不可摧的装甲以外，分布合理的点防御火力也使统治者-级能有效拦截轰炸机的高速鱼雷。综上所述，该巡洋舰已经有足够说服力证明：真正可靠的军事工程是难以被所谓的新理念、新科技所战胜的！尤其是在那些果敢且经验丰富的军官手中亦是如此。

可靠耐用，经常出没于核心世界和前哨站附近的主权领域之中。也许统治者-级就是海盗与违法者最厌恶最害怕的战舰了。
text1_095:
Ponderous and menacing, the Dominator-class is one of the most widespread system defense cruisers in Hegemony space. 

While not the most technologically advanced hull, it relies on a plethora of ballistic hardpoints to accomplish its mission, which is more often than not defending orbital installations and vital points of intra-system trade routes. A poor shield emitter which is difficult to manage and thus, rarely engaged, gives way to an almost impregnable interlocking armor belt system making the Dominator safe from most weapons. Even strike craft cannot overcome the hail of projectiles that can be launched to intercept their payloads. This hull proves that tried and true military engineering is difficult to overcome by new ideas and technologies, especially when in the hands of tough, determined crews and experienced officers.

Dependable, durable, and a constant presence in home space around civilized worlds and outposts, the Dominator is perhaps most hated and feared by pirates and law-breaking corporate agents.

text2:
星域中一块罕见的技术瑰宝。这艘速度卓越的巡洋舰凭借高效率、高弧度的尖端护盾发生器，使极光-级成为了最安全的巡洋舰之一。

人们只想知道，这样圆滑、不对称却异常高效的巡洋舰是如何在{人之领}海军舰队中创造奇迹的。此外，内置的先进磁通耗散系统，让这些依附在船体表面的幅能通道给该舰提供了深广的幅能空间。

尽管大部分用于建造极光-级的蓝图都是受到严格保密的企业机密，但依旧有少数几艘服役于{霸主}的防御舰队之中，且一些富裕的雇佣军舰长也会想尽办法从特殊渠道内购买一艘以充当旗舰来使用。

以吨位来计算，除开其高昂的造价，很少有其它舰船能超越极光-级巡洋舰。
text1_095:
The Aurora-class cruiser is a technological marvel, rarely seen. Among the fastest and most maneuverable cruisers in the Sector, it is also one of the safest due to its wide shield coverage. 

One can only wonder what the Domain Navy could accomplish with a fleet of these sleek, asymmetric, and eminently effective vessels. The shields are backed up by hyper-advanced flux dissipation systems installed throughout the hull, which gives the Aurora a deep flux pool.

Most blueprints required to manufacture Aurora-class ships are closely guarded corporate secrets, but a few have also seen service in Tri-Tachyon fleets and, rarely, in the hands of enterprising mercenary captains.

Few ships can outperform the Aurora ton for ton. Its only weakness is its prohibitive cost.

text2:
至高点-级是先进科学与军事技术的有效结合体，凭借内置的高精度传感器与勘探设备，使它极其擅长在敌对星域中进行长期探索。

舰首处的大型不对称结构被众多传感器等附属设备所塞满，以诠释其重要程度。由于至高点-级的舰长通常习惯独自作战，因此他们往往是一群独立自主、自力更生的冒险家。

通过灵活运用高效护盾以及强大引擎，使其能在一对一的交战中立于不败之地。然而孱弱的装甲使它遭受多方集火时显得有些弱不禁风，因此制高点-级很少成为大型舰队中的一份子。

高昂的成本意味着只有富裕的高科技矿业财团才能负担得起一艘制高点-级。他们通常会将其全副武装后,派遣至任何值得探索的偏远星域。
text1_095:
The Apogee-class vessel is an effective mix of advanced scientific and military technologies, perfect for long-range exploration of hostile space. 

The class features an asymmetric design with a large forward section, usually outfitted with long-range tech scanners. Apogee captains are used to operating alone and tend to be an independent, self-reliant lot. 

The ship can hold its own in one-on-one engagements by smart use of its powerful shield emitter and strong engines. However, its armor rating makes it seem somewhat fragile on paper, and thus it is rarely part of big fleet actions.

The high construction costs typically mean that only affluent tech mining consortiums can afford an Apogee-class vessel that is fully outfitted for an aggressive exploratory role.

text2:
坚固可靠且并不昂贵。企业-级常由私营公司制造，用于执行护送或被{英仙座联盟}用于星系防御。

大概是星域中被应用最广泛的民用巡洋舰。企业-级的蓝图不仅在大多数地区都能获得,且很容易到手。

作为绝大多数小型舰队中的骄傲，这艘结实可靠且泛用性极佳的巡洋舰不仅常常被用于执行重要行动，且也被一些小规模的海盗组织充当一艘旗舰来使用。尽管内置的探矿无人机能提供额外的防御火力，但由于只配备了民用级幅能核心，因此在遭到敌方战舰猛烈炮火时，它的护盾依旧很容易被迅速击垮，并使该舰遭到重创。因此它通常扮演一名可提供远程导弹支援但缺乏近战持续输出力的角色。
text3: 坚固、耐用、可靠的企业-级通常利用导弹来进行远程火力支援，但也缺乏在长期作战中所需的持续输出能力。尽管内置的探矿无人机能提供额外的防御火力，但所配备的民用级反应堆依旧会在护盾遭受猛烈炮火时被迅速击垮。
text1_095:
Tough, dependable and not overly expensive, Venture-class cruisers are usually constructed by private corporations for escort duty or by small non-aligned worlds for system defense.

The Venture-class ships are perhaps the most widely used civilian cruisers in the Sector. The blueprints for the Venture are widely available and can often be secured without too much trouble. 

When used by small corporations, the ship is usually the pride of the fleet and is used to underpin vital operations. Due to its ubiquity, the vessel also serves with quite a few pirate outfits, where it sometimes fills the role of command ship.
text2_095: Tough and dependable, the Venture is usually fitted with a good missile complement but lacks the sustained damage output needed to do well in prolonged engagements. A built-in mining drone bay provides additional defenses - a particularly good thing because the civilian-grade power generators make the shields easy to overwhelm.
text1_091:

text2:
雄鹰-级经常出没于前线战斗舰队中，并扮演着中坚力量的角色。这很容易理解：凭借完美的结构、强劲的引擎、致命的武器，使雄鹰-级对任何敌人来说，都是一个巨大的威胁。

凭借多元化的武器配置，不仅能给敌方舰队带来强劲的战术冲击，且合理的点防御火力也能轻松拦截任何靠近的小型目标。而良好的装甲与高效的护盾使雄鹰-级即使被更强大的主力舰攻击时也能安然应对。

然而这些优势在某种程度上使其很容易被轰炸机所克制，因此该舰舰长需要时刻注意来袭的突击型联队，因为雄鹰-级会轻易的在现代打击武器的复数攻击下，被迅速瘫痪。

雄鹰-级在{英仙座联盟}如此大受欢迎的原因，一方面是因为它不仅是联盟海军事实上的标准巡洋舰，同时也是大多数下级军官曾在雄鹰-级上服役过而建立起的深厚感情。

作为从{人之领}继承下来的一种灵活且强大的巡洋舰，雄鹰-级不断地提醒着人们，那些人类曾在美学与技术上所获得的杰出成就。
text3: 作为一艘敏捷的巡洋舰，雄鹰-级通过牺牲侧翼防御，来使自身具备令人印象深刻的正面火力。
text1_095:
Eagle-class cruisers are often found at the core of military fleets headed for battle. It is not hard to see why: A strong overall profile, with a robust engine, the Eagle's deadly weapons package is a threat to all enemies.

The Eagle can deliver a strong tactical punch to enemy formations. Its numerous turret and hardpoint emplacements make it very dangerous to smaller foes. Decent armor and a strong shield emitter let it hold space while outnumbered, or even when faced with the rare larger ship. 

These strengths are somewhat countered by strike craft - an Eagle captain must always watch their scopes for an approaching strike squadron, since their ship will be easily crippled by multiple hits from modern strike weapons. 

The embodiment of the sleek and powerful space cruiser from the time of the Domain, the Eagle-class ships are a beautiful reminder of the technological and aesthetic achievements of humanity's past.
text2_095: Agile for a cruiser, the Eagle is difficult to flank and has impressive and focused frontal firepower.
text1_091:

text2_091: Agile for a cruiser, the Eagle is difficult to flank and has impressive and focused frontal firepower.
text1_091cn:
雄鹰-级经常出没于前线战斗舰队中，并扮演着中坚力量的角色。这很容易理解：凭借完美的结构、强劲的引擎、致命的武器，使雄鹰-级对任何敌人来说，都是一个巨大的威胁。

凭借多元化的武器配置，不仅能给敌方舰队带来强劲的战术冲击，且合理的点防御火力也能轻松拦截任何靠近的小型目标。而良好的装甲与高效的护盾使雄鹰-级即使被更强大的主力舰攻击时也能安然应对。

然而这些优势在某种程度上使其很容易被轰炸机所克制，因此该舰舰长需要时刻注意来袭的突击型联队，因为雄鹰-级会轻易的在现代打击武器的复数攻击下，被迅速瘫痪。

雄鹰-级在{英仙座联盟}如此大受欢迎的原因，一方面是因为它不仅是联盟海军事实上的标准巡洋舰，同时也是大多数下级军官曾在雄鹰-级上服役过而建立起的深厚感情。

作为从{人之领}继承下来的一种灵活且强大的巡洋舰，雄鹰-级不断地提醒着人们，那些人类曾在美学与技术上所获得的杰出成就。
text2_091cn: 作为一艘敏捷的巡洋舰，雄鹰-级通过牺牲侧翼防御，来使自身具备令人印象深刻的正面火力。

text2:
雄鹰-级的小兄弟。猎鹰-级通过牺牲装甲来换取优秀速度,以在军方舰队中充当轻型巡洋舰的角色。

独特的'轻量化'设计并未使得火力显著下降，反而让猎鹰-级能为任何舰队提供有价值的战术支持。只要给予它适当的武装，就能让这种轻型巡洋舰不管是在密接支援还是突击方面都能轻松胜任。

猎鹰-级的辅助推进器不仅给予它优异的机动性，且能在某些危急关头起到快速脱离战场的作用。

迅捷而优雅的猎鹰-级不仅常在稍大的舰队中担任指挥角色，同时也是重要贸易路线里坚定的守护者。
text3: 尽管火力稍有欠缺，但凭借让绝大多数小型舰船都自愧不如的卓越机动，以及巡洋级别的反应堆与电镀装甲，使猎鹰-级仍能轻松对付那些以速度著称的护卫舰。
text1_095:
Often called the Eagle cruiser's little brother, the Falcon-class cruiser sacrifices armor for speed, neatly filling the light cruiser role in military fleets throughout the Sector. 

The "light" designation does not indicate a significant reduction in firepower, however, making the Falcon a valuable tactical asset to any fleet. The ship is easily able to fill a wide variety of roles, from close support to assault, given the proper configuration. 

The Falcon's top notch engines give it the ability to quickly disengage from battle should its defenses be pressed to a critical point.

Swift and elegant, Falcon-class cruisers are often found as lead elements in larger fleet formations, or deployed to reinforce anti-pirate convoys.
text2_095: This light cruiser features mobility that puts smaller ships to shame, but its firepower is somewhat lacking. However, the Falcon can still face down smaller ships due to its cruiser-grade power generators and armor plating.

text1_091cn:
雄鹰-级的小兄弟。猎鹰-级通过牺牲装甲来换取优秀速度,以在军方舰队中充当轻型巡洋舰的角色。

独特的'轻量化'设计并未使得火力显著下降，反而让猎鹰-级能为任何舰队提供有价值的战术支持。只要给予它适当的武装，就能让这种轻型巡洋舰不管是在密接支援还是突击方面都能轻松胜任。

猎鹰-级的辅助推进器不仅给予它优异的机动性，且能在某些危急关头起到快速脱离战场的作用。

迅捷而优雅的猎鹰-级不仅常在稍大的舰队中担任指挥角色，同时也是重要贸易路线里坚定的守护者。
text2_091cn: 尽管火力稍有欠缺，但凭借让绝大多数小型舰船都自愧不如的卓越机动，以及巡洋级别的反应堆与电镀装甲，使猎鹰-级仍能轻松对付那些以速度著称的护卫舰。

text2:
小巧却令人畏惧的先进驱逐舰，强大的引擎不仅赋予其优异的速度与机动性,且布局合理的炮塔,为美杜莎-级提供了丰富的战术选择。但苛刻的后勤维护成本让一些指挥官不得不减少它的出场机会,而选择部署其它性价比更高的舰船。

由于美杜莎-级与特种部队以及精英海盗关系紧密，因此使其成为这些组织中最受尊敬的驱逐舰之一。同时因原始蓝图存世量稀少，且一般只被实力雄厚的大型制造商与军方势力所严密掌控，所以现在也只能通过那些登陆过美杜莎-级的幸运儿才能准确描述出这艘先进驱逐舰所具备的尖端技术。

因造价高昂让大部分企业与政府都难以进行批量生产，使如今仅有少数几艘美杜莎-级受雇于政府军,以用于执行秘密作战任务。在极为罕见的情况下，如果该舰不幸落入海盗手中，那么通常其结果是：最近星域中所有的小型与中型的贸易商队都将急剧减少，从而使绝大数行星和前哨站的经济遭到重创。

然而对于这种潜在威胁，海军战略家也暂时没能提出合适的应对策略。
text1_095:
A fearsome ship whose top tier engines provide great speed and maneuverability for a destroyer. Multiple energy weapon slots allow for a plethora of tactical possibilities. Its best-in-class performance is matched by a demanding logistical profile that has led some fleet commanders to eschew its use in favor of other ships that can be deployed more frequently and cheaply.

The Medusa is one of the most respected destroyers in the sector due to its association with black ops and elite pirates. The few that have been aboard a Medusa can attest to its extreme level of technological sophistication. Medusa-class blueprints are few in number and are some of the rarest and most closely guarded data in the Sector.

Deemed too expensive to mass produce by most corporations and governments, it is rarely employed by the lawful authorities as a black ops cruiser. On the rarest occasion, a Medusa-class hull may fall into the hands of pirates. The usual results are a drastic reduction in system small to medium shipping, which puts a strain on most planetary and outpost economies.

Sector naval tacticians have few answers for the threat that the Medusa presents.

text2:
这种尖端的突击轻型驱逐舰，与早已声名远扬的野狼-级来自同一设计团队。因伯劳鸟-级先进的推进系统被设计成在'微驱动'操作中选择性地释放等离子体，使得该舰可在绝佳的时机突袭目标,并在目标准备反击前立即撤退，但因制造一艘轻巧且经济的船体所最优先考虑的是攻击与速度,而导致该舰的护盾、装甲与幅能的素质均不突出，并使得伯劳鸟-级获得了'玻璃大炮'的美誉。如果不想让它在战斗还未展开前就变成一块废铁，那就最好把它的指挥权交给那些老练的舰长。

因等离子爆裂驱动器中某些独特的结构元件会在富氧环境中磨损、腐蚀，因此在例行检修中，必须优先确认这些关键部位的陶粒聚合物涂层是否完整，并在必要时重新涂上。
text1_095:
An advanced fast-attack light destroyer from the same design team as the near-ubiquitous Wolf, the Shrike's advanced propulsion system is designed to selectively vent plasma in a 'microburn' maneuver. This allows the Shrike to dart into tactical opportunities as they arise, strike, and escape before a proper counter-attack is mounted. Shields, armour, and sustained flux capacity are somewhat underwhelming due to the need to build a light yet economical hull which prioritizes attack speed, leading to the Shrike gaining the reputation as a glass cannon best entrusted to skilled captains.

Certain unique structural elements in the plasma venting system are known to, with wear, corrode in oxygen-rich atmospheres, so care must be taken to re-apply ceramopolymer coating at each hull servicing.

text2:
骡子-级这块难啃的骨头不仅能轻松胜任一名货运角色，也能让遇到它的海盗们悄悄绕开，并尝试寻找下一名更容易搞定的猎物。

商人们经常会独自用它来往返于星域之间，并从事着小型贸易活动。即使在没有护卫的情况下骡子-级也能提供舰长们所希望看到的自保能力。
text1_095:
The Mule-class is a tough nut to crack, which makes its designation as a combat freighter apt. Pirates will often bypass even a lone Mule and go off in search of easier prey.

Often its captains casually ferry cargo to and fro between the star systems of the Sector alone and comfortable in the knowledge that they could afford the best protection a freighter captain can hope to get, short of an escort, of course.

text2:
基于水牛-级货舰的衍生舰种。该修改包括将幅能核心、重型装甲、机动推进器升级成军用级别，还将低效的{Mk.I}护盾发生器与大部分货舱移除。

目前，星域中不仅充斥着大量不可预测的暴力，且绝大数冲突经常都是因为一丁点的资源或轻微的蔑视而瞬间爆发起来的。由于军用级舰船有时并不能及时达现场，因此一些聪明的工程师转而对那些原本毫无威胁的民用船体进行改造，以满足这方面的需求。

虽由水牛-级船体框架改进而来，但因改造范围非常全面，因此该舰也被公认为是一种独立性质的舰船。依靠从火力与装甲两者间取得的平衡，使其在战斗中不仅能坚守阵地，还能对敌方进行猛烈还击，且非正统的武器配置与船体改造不仅能组建出一支独特的舰队，同时也意味着没有任何两艘水牛{Mk.II}是完全相同的。

虽然水牛{Mk.II}的船长会随不同的船体配置而改变战术，但因缺乏护盾发生器和重型能量武器的帮助，所以它一般不会与护卫舰以上的舰船近距离对峙。该舰的作战计划通常是一击必中的精巧策略，且只对同一名敌人实行一次，显然这种独特战术在它优秀船员们的帮助下是非常奏效的。
text1_095:
A derived class, based on the Buffalo freighter. The modifications include the addition of military grade power generators, heavier armor, and maneuvering thrusters as well as the removal of the Mk. I shield emitter and the majority of the cargo holds.

The Sector is violent and unpredictable, and conflicts often flare up over the smallest resource or perceived slight. In such situations military-grade ships are sometimes not available quickly enough. Thus, resourceful engineers turn to hull modifications in order to be able to meet the demand for war materiel.

The base hull of this destroyer is a standard Buffalo-class freighter, however due to the scope of the hull conversion, the Buffalo Mk. II is considered a separate class. The result is a fighting ship which can hold its own and fight back hard, especially if properly screened from strikes and heavier hulls. The unorthodox weapons configuration often leads to unique fleet formations, and hull modifications often mean that no two Buffalo Mk. IIs are quite the same.

The tactics employed by a Buffalo Mk. II captain will vary as much as his hull configuration, but rarely involve standing toe-to-toe with anything heavier than a frigate due to the lack of a shield generator and energy weapon emplacements. The combat plans usually involve a one hit wonder stratagem that never works on the same enemy twice, which is perfectly fine with the crew of the Buffalo Mk. II.

text2:
女武神-级是标准驱逐舰规模的人员运输舰，其充足的内部空间足以单次运载两个连的陆战队员。就其规模而言，由于较大的船体以及脆弱的内部构造，导致女武神-级也只能在近距离内依靠最基本的防御火力，来勉强抵御战机和导弹。

其配备的地面支援武器能在大气中或着陆时为友军提供火力支援，因此女武神-级通常被应用于未开化世界的袭击行动中，扮演着快速部署重型陆战队员的角色。

因拥有对地面直接投放大量部队的能力，促使{霸主}的官僚们签署了一份'限购令'以禁止出售给未授权的第三方，然而这一限购消息在生效前，就已通过大量渠道泄露到公众世界中，也使某些目光短浅的投机者们似乎看到了所谓的未来商机。然而因生产过剩与功能有限等因素，不仅让这些投机者们血本无归，且在供大于求的情况下，显然获得一艘女武神-级要比{霸主}这条禁令在家喻户晓之前更为简单。
text1_095:
The Valkyrie is a standard destroyer-sized troop transport with enough room to carry two companies of marines. Tactically it is weak for its size, only able to defend itself at short ranges from missiles and fighters.

As an atmosphere-capable combat dropship with ground support weapon mounts designed to operate during re-entry and when grounded, the Valkyrie is often used to deploy heavy infantry support for tech raids on decivilized worlds. 

The ability to deliver large amounts of troops directly to ground targets while providing fire support prompted Hegemony bureaucrats to designate the hull as "restricted" for sale to third parties. Naturally, news of the restriction made it to the general public cycles before it came into effect, launching ill-fated speculation in the future prices of this class. Thus, overproduction and the hull's limited options made the speculator's activities bets largely moot, the only net result is that now, due to oversupply, it is just as easy to obtain a Valkyrie ship as before news of the Hegemony ban ever became public.
