text1_091cn: Chicomoztoc}作为该星系首批殖民对象的行星之一。由于被选作成为一处重要的工业枢纽，因此一片规模宏大的纳米工厂群就坐落于此。这颗略适合地球化的候补行星，因早期无节制的工业发展以及受到后期战争的波及，使其原本就稀薄的大气充满了复杂的硫化合物、有机精炼副产品以及令人担忧但可控的锕系有毒粉尘。
text3_091cn: Chicomoztoc}庞大的人口都定居于由强大的政治煽动家们控制的地下建筑群中，他们不仅向失业者许诺改革和岗位，并筹集了大量的竞争性技术，甚至还收取贿赂为罪犯提供庇护伞，以便为他们自己的联盟服务。建筑群有时会因为骚乱、抗议和暴动而紧急封锁，但只要工厂群安好，并制造出足够的货物、机械、工具和船体，霸主}便只会对这儿睁只眼闭只眼。

text2: Eventide}是一颗几乎被潮汐力牢牢锁住的行星，也是理想的地球化改造的候选之一。尽管每一天，因缓慢的自转速度，导致这里的夜晚如深冬般寒冷，而白天则如盛夏般炎热。但在巧妙布置的恒星镜与恒星罩的帮助下，使这里部分区域的昼夜温度不仅达到理想水平，且肥沃的土壤也让当地的农业经济得到迅速发展，并使这的人们居住到了由宽广的贵族种植园所环绕的城市之中
notes: Leading families of Eventide pool their influence into great combines that sponsor the solar mirrors and shades which maintain islands of habilitability. The disgraced and poorest, meanwhile, live in the twilight peripheries where the harsh climactic shifts of the slow summer-day/winter-night cycle must be endured in full force. Culturally conservative, planetary media concerns itself largely with the social rituals and machinations of leading family alliances. The prevailing ethos of Eventide (or the local inheritance laws, depending on who you ask) lends itself to providing a disproportionate number of officers to the Hegemony military.
text1_095: Eventide is a nearly tidally-locked world that was found to otherwise be an ideal candidate for terraforming. Just one day passes on Eventide per year, or near enough, leading to extreme winter-night and summer-day with mild twilight periods between. Judicious employment of stellar mirrors and shades allows ideal conditions to prevail in large pockets of carefully maintained territory where the majority of the population is settled in leased urban cantons surrounded by vast aristocratic estate-plantations.

text3_091cn: 生活在{Eventide}的领导家族们，靠他们在联合体的影响力来为恒星镜与恒星罩赢得了赞助，以确保这颗星球拥有可持续发展的能力。然而，那些失宠者和穷困者则只能生活在暮光时区外围，忍受着极昼夜从极寒到热潮交替轮回的恶劣环境中。这儿的文化比较保守，且行星媒体比起社会礼仪和家族联盟的阴谋，更关注于他们自身。这儿流行的风气(或因地方继承法，这取决于你问的是谁)使这儿能为{霸主}军方市场提供份额巨大的军官数量。

text2: Tlalocan}的卫星，其荒芜的表面布满有隧道、掩体、机库、油罐、粮仓、电池组。这处重要的{霸主}军事基地，不仅将{Aztlan}星系牢牢掌控，且因离{Chicomoztoc}足够远，因此不会卷入当地的政治纠纷。
text1_095: This barren moon of Tlalocan is wormed through with tunnels, bunkers, hangars, silos, and batteries; it forms a key Hegemony military base which controls the Aztlan system without being so close to Chicomoztoc as to get caught up in the local politics.
text1_091: This barren moon of Tlalocan is wormed through with tunnels, bunkers, hangars, silos, and batteries; it forms a key Hegemony military base which controls the Aztlan system without being so close to Chicomoztoc as to get caught up in the local politics.

text2: 在第一次大拓展热潮中，以一艘殖民母舰为核心而建立起来的。由于经历过无数次改造与命名，使外界无法了解其最初的建造意图。如今这处容纳有{霸主}C-3}级军事中心以及训练设施的{Coatl}空间站，对于{Aztlan}星系来说其重要程度是不言而喻的。
text1_095: Built around the core of a seedship from the first great migration wave to the Sector, Coatl Bastion has changed roles and names more times than any outsider cares to review. At present it hosts the Hegemony military C3 center and training facilities for the Aztlan system.
text1_091: Built around the core of a seedship from the first great migration wave to the Sector, Coatl Bastion has changed roles and names more times than any outsider cares to review. At present it hosts the Hegemony military C3 center and training facilities for the Aztlan system.

text2: 因过度开采，使整颗卫星的冰岩上遍布的伤痕在轨道上依旧清晰可见，Zorrah}历来都是授权给多家超级企业执行开采作业，以满足{Chicomoztoc}内那些贪得无厌的工业设施。
text1_095: This entire moon of rocky-ice bears scars visible from orbit due to exploitation. It has traditionally been chartered to one megacorporation or another to feed the industrial maw of Chicomoztoc, which always hungers yet is never satisfied.
text1_091: This entire moon of rocky-ice bears scars visible from orbit due to exploitation. It has traditionally been chartered to one megacorporation or another to feed the industrial maw of Chicomoztoc, which always hungers yet is never satisfied.

text2: 被禁断的歼星武器所毁灭、如同火葬场般的行星。直到现在，因人为造成的火山爆发而引起的全球性风暴，将数以百万计的逝者骨灰不断地席卷至大气层中
notes: Hana}Pacha}在第二次{AI}战争期间，被禁断的歼星武器所毁灭。与第一次{AI}战争性质不同，这次的导火索是所谓{AI}开发权的审查而触发，而关于歼星武器部署的调查因在和平谈判中获得的某些让步而被取消。
text1_095: A crematory world laid to waste by forbidden planet-cracker weapons, the ashes of the millions of dead are still suspended in the atmosphere by planet-wide storms fed by anthropogenic volcanism.
text3_095: Hanan Pacha was razed by forbidden planet-cracker weapons during the course of the Second AI War (which did not, of course, itself involve AI as the First AI War did, but rather concerned the right to perform inspections into alleged development of AI). The issue of investigation into the details of said forbidden weapon deployment was dropped due to certain other concessions made during the peace arrangement.

text2: 战争在这颗卫星上留下了难以磨灭的伤痕。由于主城区上方的圆顶罩被撕开，使大量碎片与废弃物至今仍呈辐射状滞留在真空之中。
notes: 从模糊的红外读数不难看出，在月壤下某些不寻常的地形中依旧隐藏着居住区。显然这些是幸存者，虽然没有确切政体保持与外部世界的联系，不过那些漂浮的货船残骸有可能暗示着这儿的居民可能并不友好。
text1_095: This moon still bears the scars of war. The domes of its major metropolitan center are ripped open, the ejecta of debris still scattered in radiating patterns laid bare to hard vacuum.
text3_095: Vague IR readings from otherwise unremarkable terrain hint at camouflaged habitation beneath the regolith. There are definitely survivors hiding inside Killa, though no organized polity maintains open relations with the outside world, and if the slagged hulls of tramp freighters are any indication, the locals aren't very welcoming.

text2: 来自外星系的{viscacha}因受到{ChupiOrco}引力的影响而被捕获，这颗充满毒气的卫星因极快的公转速度与有趣的南半球盆地而被命名。
text1_095: A captured body from the outer system with a thick, toxic atmosphere, this moon is named both for its quick orbit and an amusingly shaped basin in the southern hemisphere.
text1_091: A captured body from the outer system with a thick, toxic atmosphere, this moon is named both for its quick orbit and an amusingly shaped basin in the southern hemisphere.

text2: '大崩塌'后，如果天苑四-乌托邦改造集团在这里的基础设施依旧能继续运行下去的话，那么这儿很可能变得更加宜居。尽管在{Yma}星系里，Qaras}的影响力从来都无法与{HananPacha}相提并论，直到后者在第二次{AI}战争中被彻底摧毁，才让此处变得繁荣起来。
notes: During the early colonial era of the Sector, Qaras and its orbital bases were a major volatiles/organics collection and processing center operated by Eridani-Utopia. After the Second AI War the entire Yma binary system was declared a demilitarized zone. Qaras, which managed to avoid devastation, was promptly seized by a shaky alliance of rogue mercenaries and brigands. It’s not quite been worth the logistical and legal conflicts for the Hegemony to mount a repossession effort. Yet.
text1_095: A habitable if cold world terraformed post-Collapse by stranded elements of the Eridani-Utopia Corporation using in-place infrastructure and stockpiles. The appeal of Qaras never quite matched the radiance of Hanan Pacha until the latter was shockingly razed during the Second AI War.

text3_091cn: 在早期殖民时期中，Qaras}和它的轨道基地是天苑四-乌托邦改造集团主要的挥发物/有机物收集处理中心。由于在第二次{AI}战争之后，整个{Yma}双星系统都被宣布为隔离区，而使幸运免遭破坏的{Qaras}迅速被流氓雇佣军和强盗的不稳定联盟所夺取。尽管{霸主}对这儿有收复意愿但后勤需求和法律冲突使其认为这是一桩赔本的买卖。

text2: 孤独的远古行星，在早期对这个星系的机器探测中，很快就确认了它并不属于{Hybrasil}星系，而是亿万年前被{Hybrasil}巨大的引力捕获而来的。因{Donn}内丰富的高纯度重金属矿藏，而被标记为拥有低至中等利益的星球。
text1_095: A lonely, ancient world which early robot probes of the Sector quickly determined was not formed in the Hybrasil system, but rather captured by Hybrasil some hundreds of millions of years ago. Donn was flagged as low-to-moderate interest due to easily accessible concentrations of heavy metals.
text1_091: A lonely, ancient world which early robot probes of the Sector quickly determined was not formed in the Hybrasil system, but rather captured by Hybrasil some hundreds of millions of years ago. Donn was flagged as low-to-moderate interest due to easily accessible concentrations of heavy metals.

text2: Balar}是一颗主要由水、氨以及甲烷所组成的冰巨星。与南极上空遮天蔽日的风暴相比，那些被水冰云所覆盖的区域确实看起来异常平静。而对于这种反常现象的研究，也仅仅停留在初步阶段。
text1_095: Balar is an ice giant composed mostly of water, ammonia and methane. The icy cloud-cover whorls almost placidly but for a single great dark storm over the southern pole. Little effort has been put toward investigating this anomaly.
text1_091: Balar is an ice giant composed mostly of water, ammonia and methane. The icy cloud-cover whorls almost placidly but for a single great dark storm over the southern pole. Little effort has been put toward investigating this anomaly.
text1_091cn: Balar}是一颗主要由水、氨以及甲烷所组成的冰巨星。与南极上空遮天蔽日的风暴相比，那些被水冰云所覆盖的区域确实看起来异常平静。而对于这种反常现象的研究，也仅仅停留在初步阶段。

text2: 遍布有冻结的氨河、冰冻高原以及甲烷冰川的冰冻世界。由于来自{Balar}的带电粒子流经常进入{Cethlenn}的磁场，使其在稀薄的大气中创造出梦幻般的极光。这里唯一可供居住的城市坐落在一处不稳定的形岩石岬上，里面永久定居的人们通过出售由季节性开采的有机物，来勉强维持生计。
text1_095: A frozen world of ammonia rivers, plateaus of water ice, and methane glaciers. Charged particles caught in Balar's magnetic field create fantastic aurora in the thin atmosphere of Cethlenn. Seasonally occupied organics extraction rigs are served by the sole permanent settlement of Cethlenn, a city built upon a unique arc of erratic rocky promontories.
text1_091: A frozen world of ammonia rivers, plateaus of water ice, and methane glaciers. Charged particles caught in Balar's magnetic field create fantastic aurora in the thin atmosphere of Cethlenn. Seasonally occupied organics extraction rigs are served by the sole permanent settlement of Cethlenn, a city built upon a unique arc of erratic rocky promontories.

text2: 与其他同胞卫星相比，Ena}的岩体致密程度要奇怪得多。由于大量因潮汐力而挤压成型的间歇泉不断喷发出冰冻气体，使这颗星球表面被大片冻结的气体川流所覆盖。
text1_095: Oddly dense and rocky among its sibling moons, Ena's surface is crisscrossed by trails of frozen gases which erupt from numerous geysers heated by tidal stress. A thin but visible atmosphere feeds the torus of charged particles caught in Balar's powerful magnetosphere.
text1_091: Oddly dense and rocky among its sibling moons, Ena's surface is crisscrossed by trails of frozen gases which erupt from numerous geysers heated by tidal stress. A thin but visible atmosphere feeds the torus of charged particles caught in Balar's powerful magnetosphere.
text1_091cn: 与其他同胞卫星相比，Ena}的岩体致密程度要奇怪得多。由于大量因潮汐力而挤压成型的间歇泉不断喷发出冰冻气体，使这颗星球表面被大片冻结的气体川流所覆盖。

text2: 贫瘠不堪且毫不起眼。拥有丰富的硫化物矿床，虽然经济价值不高，但依旧给{Hybrasil}星系早期殖民化运动中打下了坚实的基础。'大崩塌'后，因当地政府在政治与文学方面的错误决策而爆发了激烈的内战，也使这处靠近星系跳跃点的战略驻地变成了一片废墟。
text1_095: This world is barren and unremarkable but for prevalence of otherwise unusual sulphur compounds of little economic value. During the colonization of the Hybrasil system mining combines established extensive works to extract ore for the hungry furnaces of Culann. The Collapse however saw Crom Cruach's civil administration implode in the battles, both political and literal, to exert influence over this strategic point near the best jump-point to the inner system.
text1_091: This world is barren and unremarkable but for prevalence of otherwise unusual sulphur compounds of little economic value. During the colonization of the Hybrasil system mining combines established extensive works to extract ore for the hungry furnaces of Culann. The Collapse however saw Crom Cruach's civil administration implode in the battles, both political and literal, to exert influence over this strategic point near the best jump-point to the inner system.
text1_091cn: 贫瘠不堪且毫不起眼。拥有丰富的硫化物矿床，虽然经济价值不高，但依旧给{Hybrasil}星系早期殖民化运动中打下了坚实的基础。'大崩塌'后，因当地政府在政治与文学方面的错误决策而爆发了激烈的内战，也使这处靠近星系跳跃点的战略驻地变成了一片废墟。

text2: 历史悠久的著名矿物出产地{Culhan}在'大崩塌'不久后，被{速子科技}迅速且可疑的改造成一处重要的军事基地，且很快统治了整片{Hybrasil}星系而下一步则是以该基地为据点向临近星系投射力量。据传这里的武器库深处，有着基于神秘且难以理解的{AI}顿悟技术而创造的神话般的武器，尽管经历过两场战争的洗礼，但至今没有任何一名{霸主}调查员成功渗透至内部，以确认这些谣言是否属实。
text1_095: The oldest of the famous mines of Culann were converted (suspiciously) shortly after the Collapse into a major Tri-Tachyon military base which projects power throughout the inner Hybrasil system and into neighbouring systems. The deepest arsenals are said to contain fabulous weapons based on arcane technology revealed by incomprehensible AI-epiphany, though after two wars a Hegemony inspector has yet to set foot inside to confirm these rumours.
text1_091: The oldest of the famous mines of Culann were converted (suspiciously) shortly after the Collapse into a major Tri-Tachyon military base which projects power throughout the inner Hybrasil system and into neighbouring systems. text2: Culann}星际工厂早在几百年前就是一处重要的零重力炼油与冶金中心，该公司善于巧妙利用能源转换和存储技术来高效运作，并使其在{Hybrasil}星系中享有盛誉。如今这家公司名下的所有财产，以及{Culann}本身都被主打能源转换、发电以及投影行业的{速子科技}所收购。
text1_095: Culann Starforge was founded as a major center of zero-G refining and metallurgy several hundred years ago by an enterprise whose strength lay in a portfolio of ingenious energy conversion and storage technologies which enabled efficient harnessing of Hybrasil's nearby primary. This firm, its property, and Culann itself were rapidly acquired by the Tri-Tachyon Corporation which has traditionally dominated the energy conversion, generation, and projection industries.
text1_091: Culann Starforge was founded as a major center of zero-G refining and metallurgy several hundred years ago by an enterprise whose strength lay in a portfolio of ingenious energy conversion and storage technologies which enabled efficient harnessing of Hybrasil's nearby primary. text2: EochuBres}是本星系殖民化后期才被地球化改造的星球。尽管结果令人满意但瞬息万变的天气依旧将这的地貌撕裂成由高耸山峰与新生峡湾组成的世界。虽轨道镜阵列在'大崩塌'前就已建设完毕，但这里的温度依旧要比正常的宜居行星要低上许多。
notes: Shining Tri-Tachyon company arcologies tower over riotous sprawl of shantytown conurbation. Tri-Tachyon salariat are born, live, and die protected by security drones in the high city Xanadu while a desperate class of contract labourers dwell in the low city where anything at all can be bought or sold, including the law, over which Company money reigns supreme.
text1_095: Terraformed late in the colonization of the Sector, Eochu Bres is a world of peaks and fjords freshly torn by violent, rapidly changing weather. It is still colder than Terran-optimal in spite of an orbital mirror array completed shortly before the Collapse.
text3_095: Shining Tri-Tachyon company arcologies tower over riotous sprawl of shantytown conurbation. text1_091cn: EochuBres}是本星系殖民化后期才被地球化改造的星球。尽管结果令人满意但瞬息万变的天气依旧将这的地貌撕裂成由高耸山峰与新生峡湾组成的世界。虽轨道镜阵列在'大崩塌'前就已建设完毕，但这里的温度依旧要比正常的宜居行星要低上许多。
text3_091cn: {速子科技}的总部坐落于闪亮的弧形尖塔之上，与上城区外的棚户区相比，确实显得有些鹤立鸡群。这里的工薪阶层在世外桃源般的上城区中、在安全无人机的保护下出生、生活、死亡。而那些绝望的合同劳工则在丑陋的下城区中挣扎求生。在这里，任何东西都可以进行买卖，包括法律因为对于{速子科技}来说金钱远比法律更加至高无上。

text2: 这处由坚固材料所制成，并沉寂已久的环状星门是{人之领}最具代表性的遗迹之一
text1_095: A silent ring of adamantine material, derelict of a former age.
text1_091: A silent ring of adamantine material, derelict of a former age.
text1_091cn: 这处由坚固材料所制成，并沉寂已久的环状星门是{人之领}最具代表性的遗迹之一

text2:
A silent ring of adamantine material. If you know how to look - and you do, now - your sensors can detect a faint vibration from higher dimensions.

It is like a barely heard song, a door waiting to be opened.
text1_095:
A silent ring of adamantine material. If you know how to look - and you do, now - your sensors can detect a faint vibration from higher dimensions.

It is like a barely heard song, a door waiting to be opened.

text2: 当人类到达该星系不久后，就在{Samarra}的环状带上建立起了名为{Tigra}的采矿基地。随着罢工事件的持续升温，迫使超级军团将采矿权重新交还给这里的矿工们以平息这场叛乱。在经过数次矿业热潮之后，由于环状带上可供开采的矿物以近乎枯竭，因此矿工的后代们纷纷放下了钻矿机械并转向了低重力种植业。尽管如此，他们依旧保留着祖先的顽固与叛逆。
text1_095: It was only shortly after humans arrived in the Sector that mining operations were established in the Tigra Ring. Successive waves of extraction have seen miner strikes and rebellion through a rotation of megacorps given the Tigra license. The descendants of those first miners have turned to spinning low-G space farms in the depleted ore-bodies and old prospecting rigs of the Ring - and they still retain the recalcitrant rebelliousness of their ancestors.
text1_091: It was only shortly after humans arrived in the Sector that mining operations were established in the Tigra Ring. Successive waves of extraction have seen miner strikes and rebellion through a rotation of megacorps given the Tigra license. The descendants of those first miners have turned to spinning low-G space farms in the depleted ore-bodies and old prospecting rigs of the Ring - and they still retain the recalcitrant rebelliousness of their ancestors.

text2: 由氢氦所组成的一颗并不起眼的气态巨行星。但这份宁静被几十年前一名自称'揭秘者'的学者所打破，他声称该行星实际上是由一个异星生命家族所掌控，并从事着类似相位技术方面的研究，从而引发了一起小丑闻。之后这名学者被{霸主}委派到{Eventide}的某处医疗机构从事研究工作，而{霸主}则顺势将该行星的低空轨道的所属权彻底纳入麾下。
text1_095: A largely unremarkable gas giant composed primarily of hydrogen and helium. Some decades ago a minor scandal erupted over a scientist 'whistleblower' claiming that the planet is host to a family of xenolife which employs properties resembling aspects of phase technology. The scientist was committed to a care facility on Eventide and authority over low orbit given over entirely to a Hegemony military administration.
text1_091: A largely unremarkable gas giant composed primarily of hydrogen and helium. Some decades ago a minor scandal erupted over a scientist 'whistleblower' claiming that the planet is host to a family of xenolife which employs properties resembling aspects of phase technology. The scientist was committed to a care facility on Eventide and authority over low orbit given over entirely to a Hegemony military administration.

text2: 在{Persean}星系首次殖民化期间，就将{Sphinx}建立成一处{人之领}后勤中心。目的是为了利用地表下的燃料生产设施，来为{人之领}驻守于此的无敌舰队提供不间断的燃料补给，以防止地方叛乱的发生。如今这处战略驻地已经归于{霸主}的统治之下。
text1_095: Founded as a Domain fleet logistics center during initial colonization of the Persean Sector, a small AM-fuel production facility was built deep under the surface of Sphinx to provide the Domain Armada with an uninterrupted supply of fuel in case of local rebellion. The Hegemony has inherited this strategic outlook.
text1_091: Founded as a Domain fleet logistics center during initial colonization of the Persean Sector, a small AM-fuel production facility was built deep under the surface of Sphinx to provide the Domain Armada with an uninterrupted supply of fuel in case of local rebellion. text2: 曾由一种巨型设备操控着{ChupiOrco}的磁层，目的是为了制造出人工风暴将大量挥发物驱入太空后进行收集。但由于受到战争的波及，使这里的线圈、发电机、储罐都遭到摧毁，尽管一些空置的机库与通道仍具备最低限度的生命维持功能，但因气体泄漏与太阳能电池板的结垢，最终使该虹吸站陷入了坟墓般的死寂。
text1_095: Once a giant industrial machine that manipulated the magnetosphere of Chupi Orco to pull volatiles into space from the highest reaches of an artificial storm-system, the coils, generators, and tanks are now gutted, the habitats run-through by energy lances. A few hangars and access tunnels still show minimal life-support function, pitifully lingering until inevitable gas leakage and solar cell fouling leaves the station as cold and dead as the tomb it is.
text1_091: Once a giant industrial machine that manipulated the magnetosphere of Chupi Orco to pull volatiles into space from the highest reaches of an artificial storm-system, the coils, generators, and tanks are now gutted, the habitats run-through by energy lances. text2: 地质极其不稳定的星球。因没有成型的稳定地壳，使大量发光的裂隙与活火山遍布于地表，当它们与喷出的岩浆结合在一起时，就形成了延绵数百公里的炽热大地。
text1_095: A geologically unstable planet without a permanently formed crust. Glowing fissures and active volcanoes litter the surface, the magma they spew forth combining to form flows that travel hundreds of kilometers across the charred surface.
text1_091: A geologically unstable planet without a permanently formed crust. Glowing fissures and active volcanoes litter the surface, the magma they spew forth combining to form flows that travel hundreds of kilometers across the charred surface.
text1_091cn: 地质极其不稳定的星球。因没有成型的稳定地壳，使大量发光的裂隙与活火山遍布于地表，当它们与喷出的岩浆结合在一起时，就形成了延绵数百公里的炽热大地。

text2: 一处古老且干旱的世界。尽管几乎不存在磁场，但{Ithaca}依旧被天苑四-乌托邦改造集团评定为适合地球化改造的候选之一。在沉寂了数十亿年后，随这{Penelope}星系开始成为燃油业的聚集地，使得{Ithaca}和它的兄弟星{Ogygi}逐渐繁荣起来，但随着'大崩塌'的来临，也将这里推向了混乱的深渊。
notes: 地表扫描显示了几处零星的临时驻地，据推测是行星实验室，地质调查点和一些露天矿区。微型气象机器偶尔会传来一阵短暂却无意义的信号，因为这些仪器早已被沙尘暴所损毁，且毫无用处。
text1_095: An old, dry world with little magnetic field to speak of, Ithaca was nonetheless judged a good candidate by the Eridani-Utopia Terraforming Corporation. Quiet for billions of years, Penelope's Star became a hive of activity to fuel the transformation of Ithaca and its sibling world Ogygia, only to be thrown into complete chaos by the Collapse.
text3_095: A surface scan reveals a smattering of temporary emplacements, presumably planetology labs, geological survey sites, and a few strip mines. Tiny robotic weather stations occasionally emit a feeble, useless radio blip; the instruments have been degraded to uselessness by dust storms.
text1_091: An old, dry world with little magnetic field to speak of, Ithaca was nonetheless judged a good candidate by the Eridani-Utopia Terraforming Corporation. Quiet for billions of years, Penelope's Star became a hive of activity to fuel the transformation of Ithaca and its sibling world Ogygia, only to be thrown into complete chaos by the Collapse.

text2: 个头不大的贫瘠世界，表面上的巨大坑洞，是由于近期被一颗巨型陨石撞击后所留下的。由于它的兄弟星{Ithaca}正进行全面的基础设施的建造，因此，Ogygia}也被认为是值得地球化改造的次要候选之一。然而'大崩塌'的来临使这些工程都画上了句号。
notes: 一个巨大的撞击事件将{Ogygia}的整个半球拍成低于平均海拔数十公里的固化岩浆海。除了破败的基础设施，这里几乎没有人类活动的痕迹，但奇怪的是，在一处大裂谷的底部，居然躺着一艘只剩下半边残骸的攻势-级战列舰。
text1_095: A smallish, barren world whose surface bears the mark of a truly catastrophic and relatively recent impact event, Ogygia was nonetheless considered a worthwhile secondary terraforming candidate due to the system-wide infrastructure being assembled for its sibling-world of Ithaca. The Collapse put an end to these plans.
text3_095: A major impact event has left much of an entire hemisphere of Ogygia a cold lava-sea sunken some tens of kilometers below the mean elevation. Little remains of human visitation except stripped foundations and, oddly, half of a rad-hot Onslaught-class battleship hull at the bottom of a fracture-canyon.
text1_091: A smallish, barren world whose surface bears the mark of a truly catastrophic and relatively recent impact event, Ogygia was nonetheless considered a worthwhile secondary terraforming candidate due to the system-wide infrastructure being assembled for its sibling-world of Ithaca. text2: 这处被掩埋在模块化支架林、工业吊舱、居住环的废弃轨道站，很可能是在古老的扩张时期而建立的。这个曾经用于联系外界星系，建有小行星信标以及移动式炼油作业的巨大轨道站，如今只剩下一片死寂。
notes:
主反应堆和有价值的工业部件都已被掠走，从受到的破坏程度来看，当时情况应该十分混乱，且被动备份系统也在混乱中遭到破坏。由于与主体过度分离，使无法收集足够能源的生命维持系统早已停止工作。你的导航计算机发出警告：这个空间站已经步入死亡，它将在{500}个标准星历年内坠入{Telepylus}的大气层中并被烧毁。

无法登陆该空间站。
text1_095: A vast orbital station built around the core of an old Expansion-era Sporeship buried under a forest of modular hangars, industrial pods, and hab rings. This station was once the staging area for asteroid-tenders and mobile refineries trawling the outer system. It is now completely dead.
text3_095:
The primary reactors and all valuable industrial components have been stripped - and hastily, judging by the extensive secondary damage. Passive back-up systems were crippled by the process and the station too far from the primary to receive enough energy to maintain life support. A minor warning blip on your nav computer informs you that the orbit of the station is decaying and that it will burn up in the atmosphere of Telepylus within five hundred cycles.
Docking with the station is not advisable.

无法登陆该空间站。

text2: 一颗寒冷的冰冻行星。Ismara}不仅是一处绝佳的采矿地点，也非常适合作为架设质量驱动设施的发射基地，以便向内部星系发射兆吨级由石墨烯所保护的包含水与氮气的包裹，其目的就是为了补给{Penelope}星系中的宜居星球。
notes: 从轨道上望去，尽管地表线性的质量驱动轨道依旧清晰可见，但仔细观察就会发现，这些扭曲的支撑柱只不过是一些残骸罢了，其中的超导线圈与有价值的硬件早已被哄抢一空。同样，融合工厂破碎的圆顶在稀薄的大气中沉默不语，而充满死亡气息的甲烷流则静静地陪伴着这片地狱。
text1_095: A cold ice-ball of a world, Ismara was the perfect location to install mines and mass-driver facilities to launch mega-tonne slabs of graphene-encased water and nitrogen packages toward the inner system to nurture the terrestrial worlds of Penelope's Star.
text3_095: From orbit, the scars of linear mass-driver tracks are easily visible, though a closer scan reveals that all that remains are marching lines of warped support columns sprouting from regocrete; the superconducting coils and other valuable hardware have long been looted. Likewise the domes of fusion plants and factories have been broken open to the thin atmosphere and the sprawl of dead habitat grids grow obscured each passing cycle by methane drifts.
text1_091: A cold ice-ball of a world, Ismara was the perfect location to install mines and mass-driver facilities to launch mega-tonne slabs of graphene-encased water and nitrogen packages toward the inner system to nurture the terrestrial worlds of Penelope's Star.

text2: 被{Salus}的磁场捕获来的金属/硅酸盐行星。曾被用于季节性机械采矿作业和毒品交易的{Nortia，因被难民潮所淹没，而变成了一处颇具规模的{自由联盟}基地。
notes: 自危机爆发以来，Nortia}的开采与提炼中心已经呈蔓延式发展，如肿瘤般挤满了岩地的郊区。地下的采矿通道连接着地表上的通讯阵列、太阳能集热器以及压力仓。Nortia}的民事治理是建立在{Charterist}地下抵抗组织与伪装成合法政府的独立走私者联盟脆弱的协议之上。这里甚至还有一处{霸主}的大使馆。
text1_095: A large but anonymous metallic/silicate planetoid caught in the L4 point of Salus, Nortia was once dedicated to seasonal robotic mining operations and substance abuse before it was inundated with refugees during the Askonia Crisis. It now forms the strongest independent base of Charterist rebels in the system.
text3_095: Since the Crisis, Nortia's mining and refining centers have grown sprawling, tumorous rockfoam suburbs; here following mining tunnels beneath the surface, there bubbling up comm-arrays, solar collectors, and pressure domes. Civil governance is carried out in the form of an uneasy agreement between the underground Charterist resistance forces (organized in a dual military hierarchy/cell structure) backing an above-ground cartel of independent smugglers pretending to be a legitimate sub-planetary government. They even boast a Hegemony consulate.
text1_091: A large but anonymous metallic/silicate planetoid caught in the L4 point of Salus, Nortia was once dedicated to seasonal robotic mining operations and substance abuse before it was inundated with refugees during the Askonia Crisis. It now forms the strongest independent base of Charterist rebels in the system.

text2: 一处死寂荒芜的世界，尽管有着一个能产生强大磁场的金属核心，但因{AkaMainyu}释放出的离子风暴不断侵袭着{Druj}的表面，使这些壮观的高能粒子不仅带走了大量的挥发物，还在其表面留下了呈弧形的纳米铁风化层
text1_095: A dead and barren world, albeit with an appreciable magnetic field suggesting a differentiated metallic core. The ion-storms unleashed by Aka Mainyu rain Druj with spectacular high energy particles, blasting away volatiles and leaving dark arcs of nanophase iron in the regolith.
text1_091: A dead and barren world, albeit with an appreciable magnetic field suggesting a differentiated metallic core. The ion-storms unleashed by Aka Mainyu rain Druj with spectacular high energy particles, blasting away volatiles and leaving dark arcs of nanophase iron in the regolith.
text1_091cn: 一处死寂荒芜的世界，尽管有着一个能产生强大磁场的金属核心，但因{AkaMainyu}释放出的离子风暴不断侵袭着{Druj}的表面，使这些壮观的高能粒子不仅带走了大量的挥发物，还在其表面留下了呈弧形的纳米铁风化层

text2: 因过于靠近{Duzahk，不仅使这颗热木星因潮汐力而被牢牢锁定，也使向阳的那一面永远处于可达数千公里每小时风速、可气化金属的地狱漩涡之中。由于每一秒都有数千吨的电离气体被炸出大气层，从而形成了一个复杂的漩涡状磁尾，其波及的范围即便在{Duzahk}星系边缘都能被检测到。
text1_095: Tidally locked to its primary, the hot gas giant Aka Mainyu's day side is an eternal hellish maelstrom with winds of vaporized metals reaching speeds of thousands of kilometers per hour. A half million tonnes of ionized gas is blasted from the atmosphere each second creating a complex whorled magnetotail with detectable effects across the entire inner volume of the Duzahk system.
text1_091: Tidally locked to its primary, the hot gas giant Aka Mainyu's day side is an eternal hellish maelstrom with winds of vaporized metals reaching speeds of thousands of kilometers per hour. A half million tonnes of ionized gas is blasted from the atmosphere each second creating a complex whorled magnetotail with detectable effects across the entire inner volume of the Duzahk system.

text2: 被乙烷、甲烷云和氮气雾所笼罩的冰冻世界。表面由被侵蚀的水冰、充满有机化合物的风化丘以及烃海所组成。而在地幔深处，一些参杂着甲烷的液态水，衰败的放射性元素，都被潮汐力加热后由冰火山口喷发而出。
text1_095: A frozen world enveloped by a thick nitrogen smog dappled with ethane and methane clouds. The surface is formed of eroded water-ice, windswept dunes of organic compounds, and hydrocarbon seas. Liquid water erupts bubbling with methane from cryovolcanos driven by tidal heating and decaying radioactive elements deep within the mantle.
text1_091: A frozen world enveloped by a thick nitrogen smog dappled with ethane and methane clouds. The surface is formed of eroded water-ice, windswept dunes of organic compounds, and hydrocarbon seas. Liquid water erupts bubbling with methane from cryovolcanos driven by tidal heating and decaying radioactive elements deep within the mantle.

text2: 由氢、氦和星尘组成的星际云，会产生显著干扰传感器的噪声，也为不怀好意者提供了藏匿地。相对来说，厚重的星云对小舰队的影响大于大型舰队。
text1_095: Interstellar clouds of hydrogen, helium, and dust that cause significant sensor noise that may aid a fleet hiding within. The (relatively) thick medium also interferes with drive field operation.
text1_091: Interstellar clouds of hydrogen, helium, and dust that cause significant sensor noise that may aid a fleet hiding within. The (relatively) thick medium also interferes with drive field operation.

text2: 黑洞视界附近的引力是难以想象的。
text1_095: The gravitational flux near the event horizon of a black hole is extreme.
text1_091: The gravitational flux near the event horizon of a black hole is extreme.
text1_091cn: 黑洞视界附近的引力是难以想象的。

text2: 强辐射下的相对论磁化射流，通常由中子星发射而出。
text1_095: A relativistic, magnetized jet combined with intense radiation. Commonly emitted by neutron stars.
text1_091: A relativistic, magnetized jet combined with intense radiation. Commonly emitted by neutron stars.
text1_091cn: 强辐射下的相对论磁化射流，通常由中子星发射而出。

text2: A halo of high temperature plasma which surrounds a star; most ships are not built to withstand prolonged exposure to the extreme radiation bombardment from the corona and will take damage if they remain within it.
text1_095: A halo of high temperature plasma which surrounds a star; most ships are not built to withstand prolonged exposure to the extreme radiation bombardment from the corona and will take damage if they remain within it.
text1_091: A halo of high temperature plasma which surrounds a star; most ships are not built to withstand prolonged exposure to the extreme heat and radiation of the corona and will take damage if they remain within it for any time.
text1_091cn: 包围恒星的光晕，由高温等离子气体组成。多数舰船无法长时间暴露在极热的日冕和辐射之下，被持续照射会受到伤害。

text2: A storm of high energy ions and exceptionally strong magnetic fluctuations. Most ships are not built to withstand prolonged exposure to such extreme radiation bombardment and will take damage if they remain within it.
text1_095: A storm of high energy ions and exceptionally strong magnetic fluctuations. Most ships are not built to withstand prolonged exposure to such extreme radiation bombardment and will take damage if they remain within it.
text1_091: A storm of high energy ions and exceptionally strong magnetic fluctuations. <ost ships are not built to withstand prolonged exposure to the extreme heat and radiation and will take damage if they remain within it for any time.
text1_091cn: 包含高能粒子和极强的磁场波动的风暴。在风暴中舰队很难被探测到,除非是最强力的传感器。

text2: 有大量小行星的轨道区，对大型舰队的阻碍比对小舰队更大。
text1_095: An orbital zone abundant with asteroids.
text1_091: An orbital zone abundant with asteroids.
text1_091cn: 有大量小行星的轨道区，对大型舰队的阻碍比对小舰队更大。

text2: 稠密的星尘与冰块形成的环状带，导致的大量传感器的噪声可以帮助舰队藏身。不过它们没有足够的密度影响飞船的速度。
text1_095: A dense disc of dust or ice which causes a great deal of sensor noise, aiding a fleet hiding within. The medium is not of sufficient density to meaningfully slow down ships.
text1_091: A dense disc of dust or ice which causes a great deal of sensor noise, aiding a fleet hiding within. The medium is not of sufficient density to meaningfully slow down ships.

text2: 战斗后留下的,可打捞作业残骸区，并可以在内部重力稳定的位置一起漂流。
text1_095: Debris left behind after a battle, a salvaging operation, or simply drifting together at a gravitationally stable location.
text1_091: Debris left behind after a battle, a salvaging operation, or simply drifting together at a gravitationally stable location.
text1_091cn: 战斗后留下的,可打捞作业残骸区，并可以在内部重力稳定的位置一起漂流。

text2: 一团挤满了小行星的区域，对大型舰队的阻碍比对小舰队更大。
text1_095: A volume of space abundant with asteroids.
text1_091: A volume of space abundant with asteroids.
text1_091cn: 一团挤满了小行星的区域，对大型舰队的阻碍比对小舰队更大。

text2: 一种捕获大量高能带电粒子的强磁场区域。陷入其中还会使驱动场受到干扰,强大的辐射和磁场会摧残感应器。
text1_095: A strong magnetic field which traps high energy charged particles. It's extremely difficult to get any sensor readings on a fleet lurking within.
text1_091: A strong magnetic field which traps high energy charged particles. It's extremely difficult to get any sensor readings on a fleet lurking within.

text2: 这种异乎寻常的拓扑结构介质被飞船用于避开热力学第二定律限制的星际旅行。
text1_095: This topologically exotic medium of not-quite space-time is used by starships to side-step the speed of light for interstellar travel.
text1_091: This topologically exotic medium of not-quite space-time is used by starships to side-step the speed of light for interstellar travel.
text1_091cn: 这种异乎寻常的拓扑结构介质被飞船用于避开热力学第二定律限制的星际旅行。

text2: 这块多维空间非常混乱，甚至会影响专为多维空间设计的设备，最好避开。
text1_095: This volume of hyperspace is particularly chaotic, hindering performance of even hyperspace-calibrated equipment.
text1_091: This volume of hyperspace is particularly chaotic, hindering performance of even hyperspace-calibrated equipment.
text1_091cn: 这块多维空间非常混乱，甚至会影响专为多维空间设计的设备，最好避开。

text2: 这片多维空间正在经历相位偏移的混乱，导致谐振级联反应大幅波动。关于这种'超空间风暴'古老而又可怕的警告即便经历了大崩溃也依旧被人们口口相传。
text1_095: This volume of hyperspace is undergoing chaotic phase shifts leading to wildly fluctuating resonance cascades. Ancient and dire warnings of prolonged exposure to so-called "hyperspace storms" have been passed down through generations of spacers.
text1_091: This volume of hyperspace is undergoing chaotic phase shifts leading to wildly fluctuating resonance cascades. Ancient and dire warnings of prolonged exposure to so-called "hyperspace storms" have been passed down through generations of spacers.

text2: 反射和集中太阳能的超轻轨道镜面阵列。这种常见的地球化改造工具，在{人之领}扩张期间，天苑四-乌托邦改造集团}将这种技术带上了巅峰。
text1_095: An ultra-light orbital mirror array used to reflect and concentrate solar energy. Stellar mirrors are a common terraforming tool and the art of their use was brought to apogee by the Eridani-Utopia Terraforming corporation during the golden age of the Domain's expansion phase.

text2:
作为一种常见的民用设计，风筝-级空间穿梭机每天都向人们展示着{Fabrique}轨道工厂在航空工程方面的质量与信誉。'太空时代的专业典范！结构紧凑却不失美感的流线型设计，不仅确保了该空间\航空飞行器能在大气中高效飞行，且内置的德尔塔{AI}还能精确操控分布式推进器，以帮助您能享受到顺利而平缓的着陆体验！'(一则由{Fabrique}公司所发布的营销广告，内容由一对衣着光鲜的情侣和一支满溢的酒杯所组成)，除了广告词外，购买界面的超链接也赫然在目)如今风筝-级凭借强大的推进引擎和恰到好处的民用级船体，使其能快速进出于轨道空间站，但由于在失重下的机动性令人不满，因此只能等待{Fabrique}公司后续更新中是否能修复这个操控系统的缺陷。

在'大崩塌'后的危险时期里，风筝-级的豪华观赏圆顶不仅被改造成防御炮塔，且两侧明显属于过度设计的姿态喷口也被替换成导弹系统(但并不会影响其机动性)。尽管难以在公平情况下赢得战斗，但只要时机恰当，它有时也会变得意外地凶狠，或者以速度优势从海盗手里逃脱。卢德左径}甚至用配有打击武器的该舰去攻击手无寸铁的货舰，然后靠辅助推进器迅速逃离，只丢下受害者和愤怒的护卫们。
text1_095:
A familiar civilian design, the "Kite"-class aeroshuttle is the day-to-day reminder of Fabrique Orbitale's reputation for aeronautical engineering- a valuable specialty even in the age of space travel. This compact space/aircraft is streamlined for efficient atmospheric flight and boasts a grid of cleverly distributed short-burst maneuvering thrusters coordinated by a delta-level AI subsystem to ensure smooth landings (a point driven home by Fabrique marketing by way of amusing ad-holos featuring a well-dressed couple and an overfull wine glass). The Kite has powerful engines for a civilian ship of its size, though zero-G maneuverability leaves something to be desired when the special subsystem is not engaged.

In the dangerous cycles post-Collapse, the Kite has been outfitted with a defense turret in place of the executive-class viewing dome and the two auxiliary jet-pods are replaced with missile systems (which do not need to draw on the limited powerplant). It won't stand up in a fair fight, but the Kite can be given unexpectedly sharp teeth and use its speed to escape from raiders. Luddic Path radicals have even been known to use modified Kite to deliver strike weapons against helpless freighters, followed by engaging the maneuvering subsystem to make a swift exit to avoid the wrath of their victim's escort.

text2:
能提供强力火力支援的高机动性平台。由于需要护航舰队来提供保护，因此无法进行前线作战。

由巡洋舰工程学院所设计,并交给牵牛星科技造船厂生产。鹰头狮-级的出生标志着一种全新的战略打击单位成为了舰队中不可或缺的关键组成部分。其意义在于可使特遣部队指挥官能迅速集中火力，并给任何成为打击目标的突击型巡洋舰或驱逐舰造成毁灭性打击。以上所有内容均出自：人之领}的战术手册。

凭借内置于船体构造中的导弹自动工厂，使它可在战斗中利用纳米机迅速将预置的原材料转化成导弹并装填至武器中，因此使该舰拥有了难能可贵的持久性导弹火力。由于这个过程中会产生高额幅能，所以把鹰头狮-级交给会一边用护盾抵挡炮火一边开启纳米机的鲁莽舰长是极不明智的行为。
text1_095:
The Gryphon is a dedicated missile cruiser designed to provide a highly mobile platform for heavy fire support. It is not a front-line cruiser, and so operates best when provided with escorts.

Among the so-called "Cruiser School" wave of ships designed by Altair Exotech, the Gryphon was a key component of the power-projection strategy that came into vogue shortly before the collapse of the Gate system. The Gryphon was meant to allow a task force commander to rapidly concentrate bursts of specialized heavy firepower, forming a devastating hammer to the anvil of assault-class cruisers and destroyers. So reads the Domain-era tactical manual, anyway.

Of particular interest is the Gryphon's hull-integrated missile nanoforge: this fixed architecture nanoforge system allows extremely rapid conversion of densely packed, pre-formulated feedstock into a narrow range of munitions in the midst of battle. This allows the Gryphon to effectively convert concentrated mass into desired armaments, allowing for mid-battle replenishment of missile stocks. The flux output of this process is, of course, tremendous so it is not advisable for captains who are relying on their shields to block enemy fire to engage the integrated missile nanoforge system.

text2: '大崩塌'前在民用领域被普遍使用的一种由小行星矿工所用炸药，经粗劣地军事化改装制成的非制导鱼雷。经常被手头紧缺的雇佣兵、海盗所使用，同时也是那些极度缺乏军用装备的舰长们所首选的打击武器。由于{卢德左径}的'战舰'上常常堆满这些玩意，而这也给它带来了一个宛如亵渎一般的绰号：'卢德之锤'。
text1_095: This dumb-fire rocket was ubiquitous in the Sector pre-Collapse due to civilian applications discovered by asteroid miners. The go-to strike weapon of the desperately under-equipped, the Hammer is most often employed by poor independent militias, Pirates, and especially the Luddic Path. This has led to the mildly blasphemous alternative name for the weapon, "Ludd's Hammer".

text2:
这种中程反护盾导弹旨在战斗开幕阶段，迅速瓦解那些处在开阔区域内的敌舰护盾。并在暴风骤雨般的打击后，为紧随而来的反装甲火炮弹幕提供重创目标的机会。

其独特的弹药供给系统能像换弹夹般迅速更换装载有{20}枚风暴火箭弹的弹药舱。但高度复杂的弹药舱与娇气的自动装弹机让这一重装过程的失败率非常之高，因此为提高稳定性，而导致它的上弹开火等流程的所需时间高于{人之领}海军的基本要求。尽管如此，暴风{MLRS}仍是一种可怕的武器系统,因为它的压制火力能让那些过于依赖护盾,而未配备足够点防武器的舰长们做出艰难抉择，是关闭护盾来承受反装甲弹幕的打击，还是屈服于火力之下并直至反应堆过载。
text1_095:
Medium-range anti-shield missiles intended to be used in the opening round of a combat encounter to disable the shields of an unwary opponent, opening up an opportunity for high-damage anti-armour projectiles to be deployed in the immediate aftermath of the Squall salvo.

Interchangeable missile pods were designed to allow for ease of rapid reloading of the impressive 20-shot Squall salvo, but the high mass of the pods and finicky mechanicals of the missile autoloaders make the process unwieldy and the timing falls somewhat below the original Domain Armada specifications. Nonetheless, the Squall is a terrifying weapon system when deployed against shield-reliant combatants as it forces a captain with insufficient point defense system to deactivate their shields or submit to high shield flux which may lead to overload.

text2:
这种大型近程导弹系统，旨在一轮齐射中发射大量小型导弹来淹没敌军战机联队。蝗虫也可用来对付大型目标，但除非目标的护盾和装甲已被破坏，否则将收效甚微。

该武器可在一轮齐射中发射{20}枚小型导弹。其简单实用，低功耗的单体追踪系统，能在分布式运算系统的协调下完美地紧咬目标，并利用微形化学矫态推进器，来在短时间内提供最佳的机动性能。由于蝗虫的目标追踪算法基于久经考验的蜂群导弹，而这也保证了蝗虫导弹极少脱靶，并在战机飞行员的噩梦中占有一席之地。
text1_095:
A large, short range guided missile system designed to launch large numbers of projectiles to overwhelm and cripple enemy fighter squadrons in a single salvo. The Locust can be used against larger targets, but will have little relative effect unless shields and armour are already breached.

The Locust launches bursts of twenty small missiles per salvo. Robust, low-power individual tracking systems are coordinated by a distributed swarm intelligence system to enable excellent tracking of targets, while chemical microthrusters provide maneuverability for a short time. Tried and true targeting algorithms based on the old standby Swarmer missile systems allow Locusts to miss only rarely. The Locust has rightly earned a place in the nightmares of fighter pilots.

text2: 一种内置构建的纳米机系统,它可以在战斗中将预置的原材料迅速转换成弹药。由于在这个过程会产生巨额幅能，因此在承受火力压制时开启纳米机是不可取的。
notes: 开启内置的纳米机系统来瞬间补充所有导弹,但会产生巨额幅能.

text3_091cn: 开启内置的纳米机系统来瞬间补充所有导弹,但会产生巨额幅能.

text2:
来自文明时代的游轮，Huan-Gogel}440}星际线-级旨在让乘客舒适且迅速地在{人之领}星系间旅行。不仅内部设有私人头等舱、两种等级的用餐服务、零重力剧院，甚至还有用于停靠/发射的小型飞行甲板以便专门接送政府要员。当然，作为一艘民用舰船，该甲板没有任何修复与整备战机的功能。

拥有合格的前置护盾来确保乘客们的安全，并保护船体不会遭到陨石或一些太空垃圾的破坏。同时所配备的全波段热诱弹发射器和一些小型炮塔，不仅能阻止小规模的海盗突袭，还能在那些常被唤起冒险心的勇敢乘客们收取一笔不菲的'弹药附加费'。
text1_095:
A passenger liner from a more civilized age, the Huan-Gogel 440 "Starliner" was built to travel between the systems of the Domain in speed and comfort. The Starliner features private first-class cabins, two classes of food service, a zero-G theatre, and even a small landing/launch bay for exclusive use by executive-class passengers. (Being a civilian ship there are, of course, no facilities for fighter repair and rearmament).

The Starliner is equipped with a forward shield to ensure passenger safety and protect the hull from routine abrasion. Refitted for the current realities of the Sector, this ship class is routinely equipped with all-band anti-missile flare launchers as well as a number of gun turrets; this serves not only to evoke a sense of adventure, but discourage casual piracy while justifying a "munitions surcharge" on each ticket sale.
text1_091:

text2:
为了确保可观的载货量和人员运输力，Huan-Gogel}430}星云-级看起来确实有些丰满以及笨拙,尽管很难让内部的乘客们产生星际旅行的独有浪漫,但合理的票价肯定不会让乘客有太多怨言。事实上，自从星云-级被悄悄投入一线生产后,就以绝对优势垄断了星域中所有的中端客运服务。

星云-级依靠合格的前置护盾发生器来确保乘客们的安全并减少电镀装甲的维护频率。同时还配备了全波段热诱弹发射器和一些小型炮塔。毕竟作为公共客运行业，乘客的安全才是运营商的首要职责。
text1_095:
The voluminous but ungainly hull of the Huan-Gogel 430 "Nebula" does little to enhance the romance of interstellar travel but it does ensure a respectable passenger and cargo capacity for a ship of its class. Indeed, the Nebula has slowly come to dominate mid-tier passenger service since the muted reception of its first line of production.

The Nebula is equipped with a forward-facing shield to enhance the safety of passengers and extend the hull plating's maintenance schedule. And the Sector being what it is, several ballistic turrets and anti-missile all-band flare launchers have been mounted at fortuitous locations to assure paying passengers that their well-being is a top priority of the operator.

text2:
虽然{HGA-220}的第一批产品被命名为'天马'，不过如今已正式更名为更谦卑的'弹涂鱼'。尽管并不漂亮，但坚固可靠的结构不仅简化了维护难度，且巨大的舱门也其功能更加多样化,因此这种结实的舰船已经在各大殖民地中充当了数百年的低端运输业支柱。有趣的是，大部分的弹涂鱼-级实际上都扮演过一些匪夷所思的角色，比如搬运工业汽轮机的专用运输舰,或装满全息投影设备，以充当临时的、将半干旱行星美化成拥有成群牛科动物奔跑的翠绿草原,当然这仅仅只是一种促进旅游产业的小手段而已。

优秀的星际运输能力确实使该民用舰成为了星际渡口中不可替代的一份子，但因为没有内置护盾发生器所以只能依靠坚固耐用的民用级船体装甲，并利用紧急推进装置来快速规避危险并保护乘客与货物的安全。尽管被卷入战斗中的弹涂鱼-级不仅很容易被忽视且脆弱无比，但它依旧会顽强的通过后置防御炮塔来防御日益流行的火蛇导弹，并快速逃离战场。
text1_095:
Most commonly used as interplanetary ferry, the Mudskipper is indeed interstellar-capable. The ship has no built-in shield generator so must rely on its durable - for a civilian craft - armour to protect passengers and cargo. There is little hope for the Mudskipper in combat, but it is generally equipped with a rear-facing turret to foil attacks by the ever-popular Salamander missile.

The HGA-220 was first produced as the "Pegasus"-class but was soon anointed with the altogether more humble name "Mudskipper". This tough little ship has been a mainstay in backwater civilian transport for centuries, and although not pretty, the rugged construction simplifies maintenance and generous bay doors allow for great versatility. To this point, the Mudskipper's image in the public mind was cemented by a somewhat unlikely holovid sequence featuring a Mudskipper transporting a herd of bovids to a picturesque arid-terraform.

text2:
圣甲虫-级是由{速子科技}开发出的一种罕见的实验性船体。且仅有数艘原型舰被生产出来。

从前，任何违反因果论的技术都遭到了{人之领}的严令禁止，而这则禁令依旧被{霸主}延续至今并获得{卢德教会}的支持。然而,从旧星门系统到FTL超空间旅行与通讯技术，任何源自星际人类文明基础的附带产物，显然是无法控制的。速子科技}不仅总是奋斗在科技的最前沿，而他们永无止境的求知欲也难以避免的会与法律发生冲突，比如首当其冲地发展了相位空间技术，以及'时流之壳'战术系统。

不过，圣甲虫-级操纵时间的原理并不复杂，它只是避免将时空的参考系指向为当前时空而已。这种看起来像是滞缓外界时间的效果，在卢德神学家和外行人眼中是十分令人不安的。当然人们必须避免用该方式说明，以防止被专门研究这种怪事的应用时空学家听到，不然他将会来一场冗长的术语矫正会。
text1_095:
The Scarab is a rare, experimental hull developed by the Tri-Tachyon corporation. Only a limited run of prototypes has been produced.

Gross causality violating technology was banned by the Domain, and this ban is now upheld by Hegemony doctrine - with Luddic support. Nonetheless, it is the handful of fringe-examples of this technology which form the foundation for interstellar human civilization from the old Gate system (depending on one's theory of its operation) to common FTL hyperspace travel and communication. Tri-Tachyon has always pushed the bleeding edge of these technologies - and of the law - by spearheading development of phase technology. The Scarab's uniquely hull-integrated prototype "Temporal Shell" system is no exception. 

So it is not so much that the Scarab manipulates time as it avoids the normal rate of consequence of the local frame of reference. The effect, as upsetting to Luddic theologians as it is to laymen, is to seemingly slow time for the outside world. Of course one must avoid stating it thus in earshot of the applied temporal physicists who deal in such miracles to avoid a tedious correction of terminology.

text2:
坚固的重型护卫舰，根据第十四军团所实行的{人之领}设计理念，使百夫长-级成为了填补和维持战线空白区域的重要角色。

百夫长-级的价值很大程度都取决于它的多功能性，依靠充足的混合炮塔与集成的阻尼力场战术系统,使其在与敌舰正面交锋时抵抗大量火力。
text1_095:
A solid heavy combat frigate, the Centurion can be counted upon to fill and hold gaps in the line of battle, as per the Domain-era doctrine practiced by the successor-state of the XIV Battlegroup.

The Centurion is valued for its versatility due to an abundance of hybrid weapon slots and an integrated Damper Field that allows it to shrug off the fearsome firepower it is sure to face in combat.
text1_091:

坚固的重型护卫舰，根据第十四军团所实行的{人之领}设计理念，使百夫长-级成为了填补和维持战线空白区域的重要角色。

百夫长-级的价值很大程度都取决于它的多功能性，依靠充足的混合炮塔与集成的阻尼力场战术系统,使其在与敌舰正面交锋时抵抗大量火力。

text2: 怀着崇敬的装甲和武器装备的重型护卫舰。由于远行者-级极高的性价比，使其很快成为了那些不太安全的边境星域中，用于保障大宗贸易的专用座驾(或者武装护送)。不，远行者-级是在边境中奔跑着的孤独星舰，不论是在有法律统治的世界、还是在土匪漫游的世界，唯有炮塔间所交叉着的弧线，才是这冰冷却触不可及的星域里所能找到的唯一安慰。
text1_095: With respectable armour and armament for a heavy frigate, the Wayfarer does not cut close the ruthless economy that would suit it for bulk trade on the dedicated lanes where safety is guaranteed by civilized locale (or, at least, an armed escort). No, the Wayfarer is a starship for the lonely runs on the frontier, between worlds where the tough law of necessity reigns, where brigands roam, and the crossed arcs of one's own gun turrets are the best comfort to be found in the cold reach of space.

text2:
该加强版离子炮拥有在交战时迅速瘫痪敌舰系统与引擎的巨量{EMP}伤害，并产生严重损伤着弹点附近模块的电弧。

离子脉冲的非标准增益介质通过三组旋转直线加速器装置来将重子物质高度离子化，当离子团击中目标时，将会产生局部电磁场，并将周围包括传感器、燃料点火器、定位模块、计算机在内的所有电子设备带来灭顶之灾。尽管该武器会熔断某些电路，对护盾产生轻微应变，但所造成的永久性伤害几乎可以忽略不计，所以很少有人会在自己的船上装满这些玩意。
text1_095:
Built for improved firepower, this enhanced version of the Ion Cannon delivers an electromagnetic pulse (EMP) which can quickly disable enemy systems and engines, dealing heavy damage and arcing to modules near the points of impact.

The Ion Pulser's nonstandard gain medium projects highly-ionized baryonic matter in a coherent bolt via one of three rotating linear accelerator apparati. When the ion bolt impacts the target it creates a localized magnetic field which plays havoc with all manner of electronics, including sensors, fuel igniters, targeting modules, computers, etc. The weapon also fuses certain circuits, and can mildly strain shield generators, thus it does negligible amount of permanent damage. Rarely the only weapon type fitted on ships.
text1_091:

The Ion Pulser's nonstandard gain medium projects highly-ionized baryonic matter in a coherent bolt via one of three rotating linear accelerator apparati. When the ion bolt impacts the target it creates a localized magnetic field which plays havoc with all manner of electronics, including sensors, fuel igniters, targeting modules, computers, etc. The weapon also fuses certain circuits, and can mildly strain shield generators, thus it does negligible amount of permanent damage. text1_091cn:
该加强版离子炮拥有在交战时迅速瘫痪敌舰系统与引擎的巨量{EMP}伤害，并产生严重损伤着弹点附近模块的电弧。

离子脉冲的非标准增益介质通过三组旋转直线加速器装置来将重子物质高度离子化，当离子团击中目标时，将会产生局部电磁场，并将周围包括传感器、燃料点火器、定位模块、计算机在内的所有电子设备带来灭顶之灾。尽管该武器会熔断某些电路，对护盾产生轻微应变，但所造成的永久性伤害几乎可以忽略不计，所以很少有人会在自己的船上装满这些玩意。

text2:
作为远程支援武器，离子束能在目标硬幅能水平上升时，逐步产生穿透护盾的破坏性电磁脉冲弧，但较高的幅能成本限制了压制效果。

当离子脉冲发生器被交付至{Chernabog}试验场，并经过短期的射击试验和战术模拟而得出以下结论，该武器并未达到比莱空间在最初竞标时所宣称的性能且远不及委托方所要求的定位。在运输费中扣取一笔罚金后，工程师们被要求以这种武器的构架为基础设计一种射程能远到从战线后提供支援的充能型能量武器。六个月后，他们如约交出了离子束这份满意的答案。

离子束基于一种尖端的增益模式理论，这可以理解为利用高维投影以影响正常空间。尽管难以制造，但这种独特的结构却能使高度电离的重子物质以一种相干光束的状态进行远距离投射，不仅会对各种电子器件(包括传感器、燃料点火器、定位模块、计算机等)造成严重破坏,虽造成的永久性损伤几乎可以忽略不计，但当离子束所作用的目标拥有较高的硬幅能时，因带电粒子的级联堆积而干扰了护盾的常规扩散循环，并产生一种可穿透护盾层的高能弧型电荷。
text1_095:
A long-range support weapon, the Ion Beam is able to fire more and more disruptive EMP arcs through shields as the target's hard flux levels go up - at a hefty flux cost for the firing ship.

After delivery of the Ion Pulser to the Chernabog Proving Grounds, firing tests and tactical simulations concluded that the weapon system was unsuitable for the role described in the original bid won by Bhilai Exospace. A heavy penalty was deducted from the delivery fee and engineers sent back to produce a charged energy weapon with sufficient range to be mounted on combat platforms expected to be placed behind rather than on the front line of combat. Six months later, they delivered the Ion Beam.

The long range Ion Beam employs a cutting-edge gain pattern best understood as a form of diffracted geometry projected into normal space. Difficult to manufacture, this unique construction nonetheless enables long-range projection of highly-ionized baryonic matter in a coherent beam known to play havoc with all manner of electronics, including sensors, fuel igniters, targeting modules, computers, etc., though it does negligible permanent damage. Operated against a high-flux target, the Ion Beam may occasionally build up a charge that will arc past energy shields entirely as the buildup of charged particles interferes with the shield diffusion cycle.

text1_091cn:
作为远程支援武器，离子束能在目标硬幅能水平上升时，逐步产生穿透护盾的破坏性电磁脉冲弧，但较高的幅能成本限制了压制效果。

当离子脉冲发生器被交付至{Chernabog}试验场，并经过短期的射击试验和战术模拟而得出以下结论，该武器并未达到比莱空间在最初竞标时所宣称的性能且远不及委托方所要求的定位。在运输费中扣取一笔罚金后，工程师们被要求以这种武器的构架为基础设计一种射程能远到从战线后提供支援的充能型能量武器。六个月后，他们如约交出了离子束这份满意的答案。

离子束基于一种尖端的增益模式理论，这可以理解为利用高维投影以影响正常空间。尽管难以制造，但这种独特的结构却能使高度电离的重子物质以一种相干光束的状态进行远距离投射，不仅会对各种电子器件(包括传感器、燃料点火器、定位模块、计算机等)造成严重破坏,虽造成的永久性损伤几乎可以忽略不计，但当离子束所作用的目标拥有较高的硬幅能时，因带电粒子的级联堆积而干扰了护盾的常规扩散循环，并产生一种可穿透护盾层的高能弧型电荷。

text2:
莫拉-级是在{人之领}海军学说以航母作战为主的期间，用于搭载盛行的利爪-级截击机而被广泛应用的航母。尽管它的装甲能承受与攻势-级并肩作战时的满天战火,但随着海军教条转而倾向使用重型火炮，以及利用巡洋舰掩护主力舰来主宰战场走向的时候，使莫拉-级被大量除役。

随着民用版莫拉-级被大量出售，也让这艘坚固可靠的航母在{人之领}边境地带被当作移动工业平台，以广泛应用于远程测量、采矿、建筑、无人机修理等领域。甚至某些地方将其半埋在星球表面以充当发电站和临时工厂，并以此为中心建立了一处全新的定居点。

'大崩塌'后，尽管没有专门以航母为舰队主体的派系。但莫拉-级依旧被迅速的、可疑的军事化了。如今这艘如同铁锭一般坚固的航母，绝对是那些粗心的军阀和海盗们所不愿意看到的。
text1_095:
This class of carrier was commissioned during the same period of carrier-centric Domain naval doctrine as the ubiquitous Talon fighter. Armoured to withstand the fury of battle alongside the Onslaught, the Mora was nonetheless decommissioned en masse as doctrine shifted to favour heavier guns and capital ships flanked by line-cruisers. 

Demilitarized hulls were sold and converted into mobile industrial platforms for use on the frontiers of the Domain. The rugged and eminently adaptable Mora was a common sight in long-range surveying, mining, construction, drone handling, and use as mobile drydocks. Some hulls were even half-buried on alien worlds and used as armoured power-stations and workshops to form the core of new settlements.

After the Collapse, Mora hulls were re-militarized almost suspiciously rapidly by factions that did not possess dedicated fleet carriers. Today they are an anvil upon which many an unwary Pirate warlord is broken.

text2: Ariverofrock,dust,andgasspiralseverinwardtowardannihilation.
text1_095: A river of rock, dust, and gas spirals ever inward toward annihilation.
text1_091: A river of rock, dust, and gas spirals ever inward toward annihilation.
text1_091cn: Ariverofrock,dust,andgasspiralseverinwardtowardannihilation.

text2: 相对比较庞大的行星。因受到附近{Mayasur}恒星风的影响，使{Gelan}的大气层失去了部分较轻的元素而只剩下碳和硫氧化物。这里除了极高的重力，还有大量的有毒气体侵蚀着毫无保护的地表，并产生了无法控制的温室效应，因此只能用'极其恶劣'来形容这里的地表环境。
text1_095: A large and relatively massive planet in close orbit of its primary, stellar wind has whisked away lighter elements leaving carbon and sulphur dioxides to dominate the atmosphere. The death-shroud of poisonous gas creates a runaway greenhouse effect which, in addition to the crushing gravity, ensures extremely inhospitable surface conditions.

text2: 82}星历年，Mairaath}在{卢德左径}的突袭行动中被彻底摧毁。这些狂信徒把曾经令人敬畏的生态空间站变成武器，那一天，陷入绝望俯冲的轨道城市以难以置信的速度撞向了{Mairaath}的表面。如今这里只剩下满目疮痍的地表，曾被精心调整过的温和天气，也变成席卷全球的噩梦风暴，而整片天空则被充满怨恨的灰烬所吞噬。
notes: 即使被末日毁灭，幸存的人类依旧只能生活在{Mairaath}的地表，并挤在圆顶城市的废墟之中，以及被无休止的风暴所袭扰。
text1_095: Mairaath was devastated by a coordinated Luddic Path operation in cycle 82 which turned its awesome orbital station-cities into weapons thrown against the fantastically terraformed surface. What remains is a charred and broken world, the carefully nurtured weather patterns of the great Mayasuran terraforming cabal transformed into nightmarish storms that circle the globe, forever stirring the ashes of a murdered world.
text3_095: Even after its apocalyptic ruin, humanity still clings to the surface of Mairaath, huddled in the broken shells of great cities brought low, blasted by unending storms.

text2: 在{人之领}统治时期发射的无人探测器。这些数量庞大且遍布星域的探测器其目的在于：为当时的人类帝国寻找可利用的资源或可供殖民的星球，并探索未知星域。除了标准版本，其中一些变种版都是交给了全自动化勘探母舰制造而成。可能遭受过轻微碰撞，这个探测器看起来并不活跃，从外壳几处呈彩虹色的辐射刮痕不难看出，其制造时间甚至可以追溯到数千年以前。
text1_095: An example of one of the countless thousands of robot probe ships sent out into the galaxy by the Domain to find new resources to exploit, planets to colonize, and explore the unknown. Some variants are produced by automated motherships. This specimen appears to be inactive; pitted by small impacts, its hull displays iridescence from fearsome radiation scarring. This probe's manufacture could well date to a thousand cycles ago.

text2: 在{人之领}第一次大拓展热潮中被制造出来的勘探舰。除了少部分跟随第一波无人探测器与勘探母舰正常出航，其它数以万计像这样的舰船因'大崩塌'的突然到来而被永久废弃。这艘显然已经失去运行能力的残骸在带电粒子与星际尘埃的高速冲击中被蹂躏了数个世纪。
text1_095: An automated survey ship from a long-past wave of Domain exploration. Thousands of ships like this were sent in waves, some independent, others attached to (or manufactured by) similarly automated motherships following the first wave of robot probes. This apparently unresponsive hulk has been ravaged by centuries of exposure to charged particles and high velocity impacts from interstellar dust.

text2: 具有传奇色彩的勘探母舰，这艘庞大的自动化工厂是{人之领}扩张时期用于探索星域与殖民化的重要工具。因具备自我修复、自动补充任务所需耗材以及制造小型无人探测器的能力，因此这种勘探母舰本质上是一种冯·诺依曼探测器。如今这艘为{人之领}服务了数个世纪的母舰早已被烧毁，只留下一副巨大的残骸漂浮在宇宙之中。
text1_095: One of the legendary survey motherships, the quiet automated workhorse of the Domain exploration and colonization effort. This is in essence a von Neumann probe, as the survey motherships contain autoforge capacity to manufacture a suite of smaller survey ships and the supplies required to perform its ongoing mission. This specimen is burned and battered by its centuries of service to the Domain, a drifting forgotten hulk.

text2: 携带着星门的巨型运输舰，旨在为当时{人之领}的核心星域周遭，建立起能瞬间跨越整片浩瀚世界的星门。该巨舰将在长达数百年的时间内让{人之领}的璀璨文化与繁荣经济能触及到任何一片星系。为了应对潜伏在边缘星域里蠢蠢欲动的反抗军势力，星门运输舰配备了强大的自动防御系统。
text1_095: Massive starships that carry the Gates used to establish near-instantaneous connections between worlds of the Domain. The Gate Haulers would burn across space for hundreds of cycles to establish full contact with the grand culture and economy of the Domain. In preparation for the possibility of fringe worlds which spurned the Domain, the Gate Haulers were equipped with potent automated defenses.

text2: 孢子母舰的任务在于，为所有适合地球化改造的星球带来一整套生命形式以逐渐将该星球改造成适合人类居住的宜居行星。从耐寒的地衣到简单的藻类所有的'种子'都经过冷冻剂的冰冻后才被释放，随着该星球的环境逐渐得到改善，将会释放出更先进的生命形式。该孢子母舰即将离开这颗星球，当从该星系的小行星中收集到足够的材料并制造出新的基础套件后，将会向下一处目标进发。
text1_095: Seeds promising worlds with a suite of lifeforms to kick-start the processes which maintain a Terran environment, from hardy lichens to simple algae up through cryopod drops which release more advanced lifeforms as planetary conditions improve. The seedship will leave the world to gather new materials from small asteroids, manufacture a new terraforming starter kit, and move on to the next target.

text2: 将来自{人之领}核心星系内成千上万的人类移民，运送至边境星系的一种应用最为广泛的运输工具。不管是从人马座横跨猎户座，亦或是直达英仙座边境，这些冷冻舱都能尽可能保护内部人类的安全。
text1_095: This is one of the massive vessels of legend which transported millions of human emigrants from the core systems of the Domain out into the great frontiers stretching from the Sagittarius Arm across the Orion Spur. Judging by the weak but stable EM read on the sensors, many of the sleeper caskets remain viable even after so many hundreds of cycles here on the wild shores of the Perseus Arm.

text2: This class of megastructure once powered the unfathomable industrial might of the Domain, putting the human civilization well toward Kardashev type III status. It is capable of extracting energy on an astronomical scale directly from the linked star. Losing control of an active coronal hypershunt without following proper shut-down procedures can prove disastrous.
text1_095: This class of megastructure once powered the unfathomable industrial might of the Domain, putting the human civilization well toward Kardashev type III status. It is capable of extracting energy on an astronomical scale directly from the linked star. Losing control of an active coronal hypershunt without following proper shut-down procedures can prove disastrous.

text2: 一堆漂浮在太空中的货舱，可能包含些有价值的货物，甚至是被冷冻的幸存者
text1_095: A clutch of cargo pods drifting through space. These may contain valuable goods that can be recovered, or even cryo-frozen crew that can be rescued.
text1_091: A clutch of cargo pods drifting through space. These may contain valuable goods that can be recovered, or even cryo-frozen crew that can be rescued.
text1_091cn: 一堆漂浮在太空中的货舱，可能包含些有价值的货物，甚至是被冷冻的幸存者

text2: 一堆漂浮在太空中的冷冻舱，可能包含数名被冷冻的幸存者。
text1_095: A clutch of cryopods drifting through space. These likely contain cryo-frozen crew that can be rescued.
text1_091: A clutch of cryopods drifting through space. These likely contain cryo-frozen crew that can be rescued.
text1_091cn: 一堆漂浮在太空中的冷冻舱，可能包含数名被冷冻的幸存者。

text2: 一处可能被遗忘并漂浮在太空中的储物点，粗略看来应该包含补给、武器以及它设备，你可以选择放任不管或占为己有。
text1_095: A cache of supplies, weapons, or other equipment, drifting and forgotten - until now.
text1_091: A cache of supplies, weapons, or other equipment, drifting and forgotten - until now.
text1_091cn: 一处可能被遗忘并漂浮在太空中的储物点，粗略看来应该包含补给、武器以及它设备，你可以选择放任不管或占为己有。

text2: 经过扫描，这些漂浮的货舱包含了数量可观的武器装备。
text1_095: These drifting cargo pods give peculiar readings unique to the spacecraft armaments.
text1_091: These drifting cargo pods give peculiar readings unique to the spacecraft armaments.
text1_091cn: 经过扫描，这些漂浮的货舱包含了数量可观的武器装备。

text2: 在{82}星历年的{Mairaath}袭击中被摧毁。曾经繁荣的生态空间站，如今只剩一副冰冷的残骸在自身碎片的环绕中，静静的矗立于轨道之上。
text1_095: Destroyed in the attack on Mairaath of Cycle 82, this cold wreckage of the former astropolis remains in orbit in a cloud of its own debris.
text1_091: Destroyed in the attack on Mairaath of Cycle 82, this cold wreckage of the former astropolis remains in orbit in a cloud of its own debris.
text1_091cn: 在{82}星历年的{Mairaath}袭击中被摧毁。曾经繁荣的生态空间站，如今只剩一副冰冷的残骸在自身碎片的环绕中，静静的矗立于轨道之上。

text2: 这处规模庞大且残破不堪的轨道城市曾是{Mairaath}上引以为傲的三体生态空间站之一。因遭到一艘巨型油轮的撞击，导致其不仅被甩出原轨道，也将大部分结构与人类撕成了混杂着血肉的放射性尘埃。从那之后这里就被一群拾荒者接管，并迅速成为海盗们的天堂。因长期暴露于辐射之下，使这的结构强度令人担忧，但居住于此的难民、疯子与强盗们似乎毫不在乎并把这里称之为'甜蜜的家'。
text1_095: Formerly one of the three astropoli of Mairaath, this station was rammed by a Prometheus-class fuel carrier and torn from orbit on a trail of fusion fire and radioactive dust. It has since been taken over by scavengers and made into a pirate haven. The structure still comes up alarmingly hot on radiation scans, but the refugees, desperates, and bandits who call this station home have more timely concerns.
text1_091: Formerly one of the three astropoli of Mairaath, this station was rammed by a Prometheus-class fuel carrier and torn from orbit on a trail of fusion fire and radioactive dust. It has since been taken over by scavengers and made into a pirate haven. The structure still comes up alarmingly hot on radiation scans, but the refugees, desperates, and bandits who call this station home have more timely concerns.

text2: 作为{Zagan}星系中的权利中心，Mazalot}确实显得有些贫穷且不太稳定。众所周知，虽{153}星历年期间的卢德叛乱事件成功得到平息，但作为{英仙座联盟}的结盟政体之一，Mazalot}的新独裁政府为了互相迎合，而对这的卢德信徒持续打压。虽然这里的水资源比较匮乏，但这颗行星依旧是成功的地球化改造的例子。由于异常强大的磁场，阻碍了其轨道基础设施建设以及维护，但这对拥有独立思想的民众来说几乎没有什么影响。
notes: 尽管作为{Zagan}星系权力的所在地，但这个人口稠密的世界也是本星系最容易发生政变与代理战争的地方，因此作为{英仙座联盟}联结该星域松散结盟政体关系的薄弱环节，尽管偶尔会有仁慈的政府上台，但在联盟与其他主要派系之间的长期博弈中，这里的权益就会如棋子般被瞬间抛弃。
text1_095: Civic centre of the Zagan system, Mazalot is nonetheless a poor and unstable polity known for a series of authoritarian governments that alternately pander to and oppress the majority Luddic population. The planet itself is a story of successful terraforming, albeit water poor. Emplacing and sustaining orbital infrastructure is inconvenient due to an exceptionally strong magnetic field, which has done little to stabilize the independent-minded populace.
text3_095: Although a locus of population in the Zagan system, and indeed demographically significant in the Sector as a whole, Mazalot is a weak link among the worlds of the Persean League, often the site of coups and proxy-wars. Occasionally a benevolent regime comes to power but it is just as soon thrown down by some outside force in the long game between the League and other major factions.
text1_091: Civic centre of the Zagan system, Mazalot is nonetheless a poor and unstable polity known for a series of authoritarian governments that alternately pander to and oppress the majority Luddic population. text2: 寒冷、寂静、被冰川覆盖的世界。由{英仙座联盟}管理并保护其燃料设施。然而由于缺乏资本投资，使这的燃料生产一直处于产能不足的状态。尽管遭到{Mazalot}新政府的反对，但自由贸易政策的制定只是为了安抚众多民用供应商的无奈之举。
text1_095: This cold, quiet world of stony plateaus riven by sleeping glaciers has been fortified by the Persean League to protect its AM-fuel facility. Fuel production was never brought to full capacity however due to lack of capital investment post-Collapse. A policy of free trade was instituted to appease civilian suppliers despite objections by whatever the latest government of Mazalot happens to be.
text1_091: This cold, quiet world of stony plateaus riven by sleeping glaciers has been fortified by the Persean League to protect its AM-fuel facility. Fuel production was never brought to full capacity however due to lack of capital investment post-Collapse. text2: 不管{Mazalot}制定了怎样的规则，只要有足够资金维持{Ilm}里生产设施的运转，这处贫瘠不堪的冰原就能一直成为依靠出口业所成长起来的经济中心，并为{Zagan}星系的发展出一份力量。这里不仅吸引了大批来自{Mazalot}的青年来此工作，甚至还有不少{卢德左径}的信徒也慕名而来。尽管如此，当地政府依旧尽量避免与这些狂热分子直接冲突，因为无论是谁统治着{Mazalot，在这处由{自由联盟}所管理的星球里，赚钱才是首要职责。
text1_095: No matter who rules Mazalot, there is money to be made on Ilm in the factories and in the ice-fields whose exports feed capital into this poor system. The youth of Mazalot come here to work, and to send their paychecks home, and many stray from the path of Ludd. In spite of this, Ilm manages to avoid purges and war because no matter who rules on Mazalot, there is money to be made on the independent world of Ilm.
text1_091: No matter who rules Mazalot, there is money to be made on Ilm in the factories and in the ice-fields whose exports feed capital into this poor system. The youth of Mazalot come here to work, and to send their paychecks home, and many stray from the path of Ludd. In spite of this, Ilm manages to avoid purges and war because no matter who rules on Mazalot, there is money to be made on the independent world of Ilm.

text2: 浓密的氮雾在干燥的冰山上不断地下着烃雨，而山脚下巨大的{HAB}圆顶上分散着一群武装工人，他们操控大量机器人与无人机维护着有机物萃取车间与精炼工厂。如今这里所有产业都由一个曾被推翻的名为{Mazalotian}的政府/犯罪集团所统治。
notes: 这处大型资源开采点如今被前{Mazalot}政府所组建的小舰队所强占。尽管他们一直试图通过重新加入{英仙座联盟}来获得合法地位，但因他们现在与犯罪网络有着密切联系，而遭到联盟中绝大数成员的反对。
text1_095: A thick nitrogen smog rains hydrocarbons on withered mountains of water-ice that stud Salamanca. At their feet, the stained hab domes disperse armoured workers herding robot-drones which maintain the organics extractors and refineries. All industry here is ruled - from behind appropriate fronts - by an ousted Mazalotian regime/criminal cartel.
text3_095: What began as a megacorp-backed resource-extraction settlement was forcefully overthrown by a small fleet loyal to a regime ousted from Mazalot. They have sought to regain legitimacy by re-entering the Persean League, but are deeply connected to criminal networks and mistrusted even - especially - amongst their League allies.
text1_091: A thick nitrogen smog rains hydrocarbons on withered mountains of water-ice that stud Salamanca. At their feet, the stained hab domes disperse armoured workers herding robot-drones which maintain the organics extractors and refineries. text2: Kazeron}曾经是一颗拥有金属核心的气态巨行星，但因在一场古老的天灾中被炸毁，使其成为拥有丰富外来重金属矿床的星球。尽管无法进行地球化改造但它依旧成为了{人之领}一处重要的工业中心，如今这里所有的自动化工厂都归于{英仙座联盟}的旗下，并提供出售舰船、设备以及重型机械等服务。
notes: 拥有丰富工业以及军事生产能力的{Kazeron，因一直为{英仙座联盟}输送军舰与训练有素的军官，使这里成为了联盟不可或缺的组成部分。
text1_095: The metal-rich core of a former gas giant whose body was blasted away in some ancient celestial catastrophe, Kazeron is rich in exotic heavy metals. Although unterraformable, this made it a prime spot for the Domain to emplace a cluster of autofactories to feed the Persean frontier's need for ships, equipment, and heavy machinery.
text3_095: The Persean League world of Kazeron always pays its dues in warships - and highly trained officers to command them. Kazeron has a rich tradition of industry and military production which makes it the crux of Persean League power.
text1_091: The metal-rich core of a former gas giant whose body was blasted away in some ancient celestial catastrophe, Kazeron is rich in exotic heavy metals. Although unterraformable, this made it a prime spot for the Domain to emplace a cluster of autofactories to feed the Persean frontier's need for ships, equipment, and heavy machinery.
text3_091: The Persean League world of Kazeron always pays its dues in warships - and highly trained officers to command them. Kazeron has a rich tradition of industry and military production which makes it the crux of Persean League power.

text2: 没有大气层的荒芜世界，因其异常活跃的超级火山群而闻名于世。
notes: 丰富的矿石是从{extracted}超级火山群周边分散的专营矿区挖掘出来的而主要的定居点基本都建立在已经休眠的死火山下方，里面居住着一些自由机器骑师与技术支持人员。这颗星球与其它多处工业区都是由{Kazeron}所主导的工业综合体协议管理。
text1_095: A barren world notable for a cluster of unusually active hyper-volcanos, the Grettir. A thin atmosphere is regenerated entirely through volcanism.
text3_095: Rich ores are extracted from scattered franchise mines dug around the base of the Grettir hyper-volcano cluster. The main settlement is built on a dormant spur and populated largely by freelance robo-jockeys and support staff. The planet is ruled by common agreement among several Kazeron-dominated industrial combines.
text1_091: A barren world notable for a cluster of unusually active hyper-volcanos, the Grettir. A thin atmosphere is regenerated entirely through volcanism.
text3_091: Rich ores are extracted from scattered franchise mines dug around the base of the Grettir hyper-volcano cluster. The main settlement is built on a dormant spur and populated largely by freelance robo-jockeys and support staff. The planet is ruled by common agreement among several Kazeron-dominated industrial combines.
text1_091cn: 没有大气层的荒芜世界，因其异常活跃的超级火山群而闻名于世。
text3_091cn: 丰富的矿石是从{extracted}超级火山群周边分散的专营矿区挖掘出来的而主要的定居点基本都建立在已经休眠的死火山下方，里面居住着一些自由机器骑师与技术支持人员。这颗星球与其它多处工业区都是由{Kazeron}所主导的工业综合体协议管理。

text2: 由于{Thule}星系里充斥着大量勘探者以及小矿商，他们为了摆脱{Kazeron}军政统治者的强权，而在被气云与矿石所包围的环状带上建起了{Thulian}空间站以寻求独立。如今这些团结一心的人们，为寻求更大的利益而开始干起非法的勾当，因此只要这片星系有人居住，这些来自{Thulian}的掠夺者就会让{Kazeron}的统治者头痛不已。
text1_095: The Thule system is riddled with prospectors and small-time miners who've escaped the oppressive power-mongering of the Kazeron Stratocracy, searching for independence among the ore and volatiles of the many ring systems. Sometimes these free-agents band together and turn to richer prizes - thus have the Thulian Raiders plagued Kazeron for nearly as long as the system has been inhabited by humans.
text1_091: The Thule system is riddled with prospectors and small-time miners who've escaped the oppressive power-mongering of the Kazeron Stratocracy, searching for independence among the ore and volatiles of the many ring systems. Sometimes these free-agents band together and turn to richer prizes - thus have the Thulian Raiders plagued Kazeron for nearly as long as the system has been inhabited by humans.
text1_091cn: 由于{Thule}星系里充斥着大量勘探者以及小矿商，他们为了摆脱{Kazeron}军政统治者的强权，而在被气云与矿石所包围的环状带上建起了{Thulian}空间站以寻求独立。如今这些团结一心的人们，为寻求更大的利益而开始干起非法的勾当，因此只要这片星系有人居住，这些来自{Thulian}的掠夺者就会让{Kazeron}的统治者头痛不已。

text2: 拥有超大质量的岩质行星，尽管具有丰富的矿床，但因极高的重力、剧烈的地震、大量可随时爆发的火山、以及陨石的袭击，不仅阻碍了人类在此定居，甚至是经济资源的开采都是极其困难的。
text1_095: A supermassive terrestial world, the crushingly high gravity of Horn prevents both human habitation and economical resource extraction. Not that there would be much desirable anyway on this world of violent quakes, massive slumbering calderas, and endless ash plains pock-marked by meteor impacts.
text1_091: A supermassive terrestial world, the crushingly high gravity of Horn prevents both human habitation and economical resource extraction. Not that there would be much desirable anyway on this world of violent quakes, massive slumbering calderas, and endless ash plains pock-marked by meteor impacts.
text1_091cn: 拥有超大质量的岩质行星，尽管具有丰富的矿床，但因极高的重力、剧烈的地震、大量可随时爆发的火山、以及陨石的袭击，不仅阻碍了人类在此定居，甚至是经济资源的开采都是极其困难的。

text2: 很可能是在该星系形成的早期，因{Horn}遭到其它天体的剧烈撞击，使分离出的物质最终形成了如今的{Athulf}卫星。不像其母行星{Horn}那样令人厌恶，拥有同样丰富矿床的{Athulf}则要温和许多。因此才成为本星系最早被殖民化的星球之一。
notes: Athulf}在传统上被认为是{Fikenhild}国王的私人财产，来为其不富裕的国王提供大量收入。聪明的{Athulf}臣民们也自发的构成了一股重要的支持力量，来为善待他们的当权国王提供重要的选举票数。当然，随着越发奢靡的宫廷服饰，王权终将会逐渐遗忘应尽的贵族义务，当罢工与暴乱打破{Athulf}的平静时，这就意味着{Westernesse}星系将很快迎来新王的登基。
text1_095: A remnant, perhaps, from the early and violent cycles of the formation of Horn, the moon Athulf is of like composition and provides convenient access to the ores and heavy metals inaccessible on its sullen parent. Humanity availed itself of the gift thus presented from the early days of Domain colonization of the Sector.
text3_095: Athulf is traditionally considered a personal possession of whoever happens to be the King of Fikenhild, and offers important income for kings not otherwise wealthy. Court dress is extravagent and the noblesse oblige of kingship is demanding. The subjects of Athulf also form an important core of support, and treated well offer a strong voting block to a sitting king. However when strikes and riots ravage the rich mines of Athulf, it is a clear sign that Westernesse will soon have a new king.

text2: 这颗小小的海洋行星不仅是{Westernesse}星系的政治中心，也是联盟中最富代表性的结盟政体之一，无论昼夜，Fikenhild}那五座宏伟的雕塑总是在其海平面上熠熠生辉，且数十家竞争激烈的全息娱乐工作室的名声也响彻内外。
notes: The system of Westernesse is traditionally ruled by a popularly elected 'king' whose holding of court - handling of certain primary executive and judicial functions - is broadcast in the local system as entertainment. It is considered essential that the King of Westernesse be wise, just, and above all entertaining. Most potential excesses of the system are constrained by a culture of alternately raucous and sentimental audience participation segments; the King is powerful, yes, but the hearts of the people are mercurial and may be moved against the King by a sufficiently compelling counter-narrative.
text1_095: This small ocean-moon is the political center of the system, seat of the King of Westernesse, and representative to the League. The five great floating arcologies of Fikenhild glitter night and day, and are notable for hosting a couple dozen highly competitive holo-entertainment studios.

text1_091cn: 这颗小小的海洋行星不仅是{Westernesse}星系的政治中心，也是联盟中最富代表性的结盟政体之一，无论昼夜，Fikenhild}那五座宏伟的雕塑总是在其海平面上熠熠生辉，且数十家竞争激烈的全息娱乐工作室的名声也响彻内外。
text3_091cn: Westernesse}星系采用的是由传统民选而来的'国王'进行统治，他将主持法庭，处理重要行政与司法职能，并担任本星系的娱乐节目主角。人们认为，Westernesse}的国王必须是明智、公正，最重要的是要有娱乐精神，因为在该星系中所做出的任何出格行为都将受到一种文化的制约，而该文化的制定者或称为观众则大多都富有种族色彩却又多愁善感。是的，国王是强大的，但人民的心也是善变的。

text2: Suddene}虽是一颗缺乏封闭式水文循环的沙漠行星，但仍被第一次抵达该星系的天苑四-乌托邦改造集团归类为次要适合地球化改造的候选者。但不幸的是，在'大崩塌'前的地球化改造中，所形成的海洋如今正缓慢渗入深层含水层，并导致其面积越来越小且海水盐度更高，而在此种恶劣海洋环境下生存的磷虾也开始逐渐步入灭绝。据估计，该行星的生态系统将在一两个世纪内彻底崩溃。在{Fikenhild}的全息小说中，Suddene}的原住民通常都被描绘成背负着宿命的浪漫主义者。
notes: 因当地政府将所有资源都集中在纯粹的生存上，所以过去曾用于进行地球化改造的水上列车与收集冰彗星的空间站均在'大崩塌'后被迅速拆解回收。由于当地缺乏必备的基础居住设施，导致{Suddene}只得不情愿的屈服于{Fikenhild}所制定的经济规则与政治事务。而最近{Westernesse}星系的国王因开放了投票权，而将{Suddene}内的反对派变成了政治制度的顽固破坏者。
text1_095: Categorized as a secondary terraforming candidate by the first surveys of the system, Suddene is a desert world lacking a closed hydrological cycle. The seas formed during pre-Collapse terraforming are slowly seeping into deep aquifers, becoming smaller, saltier, and toxic to each succeeding meta-generation of genemod krill. Estimates put total ecological collapse at only a century or two off. Natives of Suddene are typically portrayed as fatalistic romantics in Fikenhild's holo-novels.
text3_095: The terraforming of Suddene and attendant trains of water-bearing comets were rapidly abandoned post-Collapse as the remaining authorities focused resources on pure survival. Lacking infrastructure and population, Suddene has always been begrudgingly subservient to Fikenhild in economic and political matters. Reforms by one recent King of Westernesse have opened up the voting franchise and turned Suddene's bitter rebels into the recalcitrant spoilers of system politics.

text2: 一处寒冷且令人生畏的世界，尽管如此，由于其现存的火山活动，让{Ailmar}在很久以前就被一艘孢子母舰选中并被播种。当第一批人类达到{Westernesse}星系时，他们就发现了这处被冰雪侵蚀且死寂沉沉的苔原行星，但奇迹的是，在其火山周边的山谷与峡谷间却仍保留有成片的落叶松林。尽管{Ailmar}的生活异常艰苦且困难重重，但仍是一个充满活力的世界.
notes: 在工业崩溃前，Ailmar}就已在{Westernesse}星系中保持独立，并以妥协的方式来应对各种体制外的竞争势力的觊觎.比如{卢德教会}、海盗甚至是臭名昭著的{Leonis}军阀所组建的临时联盟。而在{Fikenhild}的全息娱乐小说中，Ailmar}里的人通常都被描绘成既坚忍又狡诈的反派。
text1_095: A cold and forbidding world, Ailmar nonetheless was selected for seeding by an early sporeship due to extant volcanism. When humans arrived in the Westernesse system, they found a world of lifeless highlands worn smooth by ice-storms. But life found small valleys and canyons, and even forests of genmod larch-6 clustered in volcanic provinces. Living is tough on Ailmar, but it is a world alive despite hardship.
text3_095: Industrialized pre-Collapse, Ailmar has been able to maintain its independence from the Kingdom of Westernesse by compromising with various competing out-of-system powers, including the Luddic Church and occasionally pirates, notoriously including a temporary alliance with the Warlord Leonis. The Ailmarene are the go-to antagonist in Fikenhild's holo-entertainment, portrayed as stoic as they are treacherous.

text2:
小巧、寒冷、但适宜居住的星球，由于被当时{人之领}的殖民规划者评定为'微不足道'，因此这里也仅仅保留了一处古老的燃料生产设施。有趣的是，
在{Madeira}的地表上，那些被大规模风暴所席卷过的冰层裂缝中，发现了一些荧光伪藻以及奇异的挥发物。
notes: 鉴于{Madeiran}总是依靠外部的经济援助，因此这里对{人之领}的忠诚是毋庸置疑的。随着'大崩塌'的到来，这个人口不多的世界，成为了{英仙座联盟}创始成员之一。
text1_095: A small and cold but just-habitable world deemed insignificant enough by Domain colonization planners to harbour a fuel production facility. Otherwise notable for exotic volatiles captured from its primary and the fluorescing pseudo-algaes which live within the cracks of vast storm-swept ice-fields that dominate the surface of Madeira.
text3_095: Knowing that Madeira would always rely on outside resources for survival, the Domain would count on the polity's loyalty. The Collapse was not accounted for in this equation, however, and the Madeiran polity was among the founding members of the Persean League despite its modest population and limited industry.

text2: 主要由氢与氦所组成的热木星，因过于靠近其母恒星，且{Satanazes}的大气外层是由一氧化碳与碱金属构成,所以才形成了如愤怒人脸般的黑色斑纹.
text1_095: A hot gas giant primarily composed of hydrogen and helium gases, though due to proximity to its primary star the upper cloud layers of Satanazes are formed of carbon monoxide and alkali metals resulting in a dark, glowering appearance.
text1_091: A hot gas giant primarily composed of hydrogen and helium gases, though due to proximity to its primary star the upper cloud layers of Satanazes are formed of carbon monoxide and alkali metals resulting in a dark, glowering appearance.

text2: Canaria}是一颗被稀薄的水、氨和甲烷云所覆盖的冰巨星。在地壳深处，因重力产生的巨大压力使其足以形成一个金属氢的核心。由于该行星处在{Tyle}与{Antillia}一处不寻常的重力稳定点上，才使{Canaria}在这种独特的双星系统中保持稳定。
text1_095: Canaria is an ice giant cloaked in thin clouds of water, ammonia and methane. Within the depths, gravity generates enough pressure to form a core of metallic hydrogen. The planet rests in an unusual point of gravitational stability in the L4 of Antillia, the minor partner of the Tyle binary system.

text2: 一个古老的世界。地表上遍布着的古火山，由于长期受到侵蚀，如今不仅难以辨认且形成了一片广袤的沙漠地区。因地下含水层保留有一定的水资源，所以一些罕见的峡谷地区仍被珍贵的植被所覆盖。
notes: 数世纪以前，一艘人类殖民初期的古代孢子母舰遇到了{Cibola，因其生态环境相对平衡且凉爽潮湿，所以才被该孢子母舰定性为可殖民。不幸的是，在随后的数个世纪中，Cibola}的地貌条件迅速恶化，直至抵达英仙座星区的第一批殖民者的到来，才发现它已几乎垂死，随后这里仅诞生了一个卑微的、落后的、绝望的人类文明，直至今日，由于这里的条件几乎没有任何改善，而导致大多数的{Cibola}人已经背井离乡，如今这里仅存着一批希望离开此地却穷困潦倒的人们。
text1_095: An ancient world spotted with stumps of ancient volcanoes worn by hot, dry winds into a world-ocean of sand. A few underground aquifers remain to feed at least one small, salty sea and the rare chasm sheltering wisps of vegetation.
text3_095: Many cycles ago, an ancient sporeship from the early days of human colonization encountered Cibola. An anomalous series of icy bodies had impacted the world, leaving it cooler and wetter than its equilibrium state and therefore within the sporeship's colonization parameters. No history has survived of the subsequent cycles, but the late Domain colonizers who arrived in the Persean Sector found a dying world populated by a small, backward, and desperate human civilization clinging to survival. The situation is little improved since re-contact, and most Cibolans have left their home world - or wish they could.

text2: 超新星爆发后，由星际空间中的气体与尘埃所结合成的一团巨大的云雾状天体。之后，在引力与辐射的不断作用下，使这团星云慢慢收缩、聚集、并最终在某一天诞生出一颗新的恒星。由于这片星云是最近才形成的，里面除了正快速燃烧的不稳定恒星以外，基本不会出现具备维持生命的世界。
text1_095: An enormous cloud of particles formed from gases of the interstellar medium or material shed by the death throes of stars. Perturbations caused by gravity and radiation create areas of greater density that may slowly gather mass to someday birth new celestial bodies. This region of space is filled with recently formed, quick-burning stars and is less likely to harbour naturally life-sustaining worlds.

Perturbations caused by gravity and radiation create areas of greater density that may slowly gather mass to someday birth new celestial bodies. This region of space is filled with recently formed, quick-burning stars and is less likely to harbour naturally life-sustaining worlds.
text1_091cn: 超新星爆发后，由星际空间中的气体与尘埃所结合成的一团巨大的云雾状天体。之后，在引力与辐射的不断作用下，使这团星云慢慢收缩、聚集、并最终在某一天诞生出一颗新的恒星。由于这片星云是最近才形成的，里面除了正快速燃烧的不稳定恒星以外，基本不会出现具备维持生命的世界。

text2: 尽管在天苑四-乌托邦改造集团的调查报告中，Yama}仅仅被评为最低级别的殖民价值，但因附近{Nachiketa}上燃料设施的兴建，促使了该行星迎来了殖民化热潮。不幸的是，在经历过第一次{AI}战争的破坏之后，使这彻底成为了一颗不受重视的次级宜居行星。
text1_095: Yama scored only marginal viability on the Eridani-Utopia Corporation survey charts, but the nearby fuel facility on Nachiketa prompted terraforming and colonization. It remains a sub-par world, in lingering decline after the devastation of the First AI War.
text1_091: Yama scored only marginal viability on the Eridani-Utopia Corporation survey charts, but the nearby fuel facility on Nachiketa prompted terraforming and colonization. It remains a sub-par world, in lingering decline after the devastation of the First AI War.
